        YOUR_KIND_HAS_AWAKENED_ME_AND_THIS_TIME                                 = 11003,  -- Your kind has awakened me...and this time, you will be destroyed!
        YOU_CANNOT_STOP_ME_VANA_DIEL_WILL_BE_3                                  = 11004,  -- You cannot stop me. Vana'diel will be the grave for you and all your kind!
        WAS_THAT_A_PHANTOM_AN_IMAGE_OF_THE                                      = 11005,  -- Was that a phantom? An image...of the Shadow Lord?
        THE_SHADOW_LORD_IT_CAN_T_BE_HIS_3                                       = 11006,  -- The Shadow Lord? It can't be! His powers can't have returned!
        THEN_IT_IS_TRUE_THE_BEASTMEN_ARE_TRYING_3                               = 11007,  -- Then it is true. The beastmen are trying to bring the Shadow Lord back.
        YOU_BE_CAREFUL_TOO                                                      = 11008,  -- You be careful, too.
        SHOO_SHOO_KEEP_YOUR_GRIMY_CLAWS_OFF_OF                                  = 11009,  -- Shoo! Shoo! Keep your grimy claws off of Windurst Orastery minister, Ajido-Marujido!
        YOU_ARE_A_FOOL_FOR_COMING_HERE_TO                                       = 11010,  -- You are a fool for coming here to the throne room...alone.
        YOU_SAY_YOU_ARE_THE_WINDURST_ORASTERY_MINISTER                          = 11011,  -- You say you are the Windurst Orastery minister, Ajido-Marujido?
        GAWK_ORASTERY_MINISTER_AND_I_AM_AVIATORY_MINISTER                       = 11012,  -- Gawk! Orastery minister? And I am Aviatory minister! How do we know what you speak is not lies? Gawk!
        I_SHOULD_CUT_YOU_UP_AND_SEND_YOU                                        = 11013,  -- I should cut you up and send you to Heavens Tower! Gawk! Gawk!
        KAHK_SILENCE_OUR_LITTLE_FRIEND_CAME_ALL_THE                             = 11014,  -- Kahk! Silence... Our little friend came all the way from Windurst to greet us. Let us hear what he has to say.
        KAHK_KA_KA_YOU_CAME_ALL_THIS_WAY                                        = 11015,  -- Kahk-ka-ka! You came all this way to ask about the Full Moon Fountain?
        WELL_YOU_TARTUTARU_HAVE_PROBABLY_ALREADY_REALIZED_WHY                   = 11016,  -- Well, you Tartutaru have probably already realized why the Horutoto Ruins were built and why the Full Moon Fountain exists underneath them.
        THOSE_RUINS_ARE_EVIL                                                    = 11017,  -- Those ruins are evil.
        THE_TOWERS_SPONGE_DRY_THE_AREAS_AROUND_SARUTABARUTA                     = 11018,  -- The towers sponge dry the areas around Sarutabaruta of all their magic.
        YOU_THINK_THAT_WE_YAGUDO_ARE_THE_CAUSE                                  = 11019,  -- You think that we Yagudo are the cause of these wastelands, but you only have yourselves to thank. You--the Tarutaru that activated those towers!
        THE_TOWERS_ARE_ALL_DAMAGED_HOW_DO_YOU                                   = 11020,  -- The towers are all damaged! How do you explain magic still being drained from the plains of Sarutabaruta?
        WHAT_ABOUT_YOU_YAGUDO_WHAT_ARE_THOSE_THINGS                             = 11021,  -- What about you Yagudo? What are those things that you continue digging? Those stones...maybe they are the cause of all this?
        KAHK_KA_KA_I_COMMEND_YOU_ON_YOUR                                        = 11022,  -- Kahk-ka-ka...I commend you on your perceptiveness.
        BUT_THE_REASON_SARUTABARUTA_IS_BECOMING_A_WASTELAND                     = 11023,  -- But the reason Sarutabaruta is becoming a wasteland has nothing to do with those stones.
        THAT_NIGHT_TWENTY_YEARS_AGO_WHEN_WE_WERE                                = 11024,  -- That night, twenty years ago, when we were defeated by your armies, you made a grave mistake...
        KAHK_KAHK_YOU_STILL_DO_NOT_UNDERSTAND                                   = 11025,  -- Kahk! Kahk! You still do not understand?
        MAKE_YOUR_WAY_DEEP_INTO_THE_CENTRAL_TOWER                               = 11026,  -- Make your way deep into the central tower of the Horutoto Ruins. There you will see first hand what the Star Sibyl and those summoners really did.
        THE_MOON_AND_THE_STARS_NO_LONGER_SMILE                                  = 11027,  -- The moon and the stars no longer smile upon Windurst. Now, the world shall kneel before the Yagudo!
        THE_BUSHIN_S_SO_OLD_THAT_HE_S                                           = 11028,  -- The bushin's so old that he's losing his eyesight!?
        SIGH_WELL_IT_HAS_BEEN_THIRTY_YEARS_JUST                                 = 11029,  -- <Sigh> Well, it has been thirty years. Just look at me. I'm not as young as I used to be.
        AH_THOSE_WERE_THE_DAYS                                                  = 11030,  -- Ah, those were the days...
        WHAT_S_THIS_YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_WHAT                                       = 11031,  -- What's this? You want to know what would impress the bushin? Hmmm... Well, when I was still his disciple, I once presented him with %.
        HE_WAS_SO_PLEASED_THAT_HE_DIDN_T                                        = 11032,  -- He was so pleased that he didn't just let me see the %, he let me try it on! I could feel the weight of the souls of all the bushin that had worn it before me.
        BUT_THAT_WEIGHT_WAS_TOO_GREAT_FOR_ME                                    = 11033,  -- But that weight was too great for me, and ever since that day, I've been striving to improve my skills.
        BUT_EVEN_NOW_I_DON_T_THINK_I                                            = 11034,  -- But even now I don't think I could even grasp that belt with my own hands, let alone tie it around my waist. I still have much to learn...
        HOW_MANY_ROUNDS_HAVE_WE_GONE_NOW                                        = 11035,  -- ... How many rounds have we gone now, %...?
        I_REMEMBER_EVERY_SINGLE_BLOW_EVERY_TINY_SHIFT                           = 11036,  -- I remember every single blow, every tiny shift of your stance. I can't tell you how much I look forward to our little matches, heh heh heh.
        BUT_YOU_KNOW_I_NEVER_IMAGINED_ANYONE_WOULD                              = 11037,  -- But you know, I never imagined anyone would conquer all the challenges I set before him/her]. Goes to show that even old Maat can be taught a thing or two!
        NOW_I_CAN_T_LET_SUCH_A_GREAT                                            = 11038,  -- Now, I can't let such a great hero go home empty-handed. I've decided to grant you any one wish you ask of me. Don't get too exotic, though. I'm just an old man, not some Far Eastern genie!
        COME_ON_THEN_NO_NEED_TO_BE_SHY                                          = 11039,  -- Come on, then. No need to be shy. What's it to be?
        TAKE_OFF_MY_HAT_ARE_YOU_SURE_THAT                                       = 11040,  -- ...! Take off my hat!? Are you sure that's want you want? Not much exciting going on under an old man's cap!
        IT_S_NOT_TOO_LATE_TO_CHANGE_YOUR                                        = 11041,  -- It's not too late to change your mind, you know.
        THERE_MUST_BE_SOMETHING_ELSE_YOU_WANT_A                                 = 11042,  -- There must be something else you want. A lifetime supply of Goblin chocolate? Afternoon tea with Princess Claidie? %, perhaps? Or maybe %?
        NO_YOU_VE_MADE_UP_YOUR_MIND_IT                                          = 11043,  -- No? You've made up your mind, it seems. Young people these days--no imagination.
        BUT_IF_THAT_S_WHAT_YOU_REALLY_WANT                                      = 11044,  -- But if that's what you really want, it makes things easy for me, I suppose. I'll give you one last chance to change your wish...
        WELL_ALRIGHTY_THEN                                                      = 11045,  -- Well, alrighty then.
        ARE_YOU_READY                                                           = 11046,  -- Are you ready?
        TRY_NOT_TO_BLINK                                                        = 11047,  -- Try not to blink...
        HEH_HEH_HEH_ARE_YOU_HAPPY_NOW_BET                                       = 11048,  -- Heh heh heh. Are you happy now? Bet you're thinking you should've changed your mind when you had the chance, huh?
        AW_DON_T_LOOK_SO_DISAPPOINTED_YOU_THINK                                 = 11049,  -- Aw, don't look so disappointed, %. You think I'd let you walk away with nothing but an eyeful of my wrinkled noggin?
        EVEN_THE_MIGHTIEST_OAK_WILL_WITHER_WITH_THE                             = 11050,  -- Even the mightiest oak will wither with the passing of time. Its vibrant leaves will fade to brown, and crumble into dust. I, too, will one day have to leave this garden behind for good.
        DO_YOU_UNDERSTAND_WHAT_I_M_TRYING_TO                                    = 11051,  -- Do you understand what I'm trying to say?
        WHEN_THAT_TIME_COMES_I_WANT_YOU_TO                                      = 11052,  -- When that time comes, I want you to take up this cap and become the mighty oak. Watch over the saplings as they reach towards the sky. I know you're up to the task, %.
        DO_I_HAVE_YOUR_WORD                                                     = 11053,  -- Do I have your word?
        WELL_THAT_TAKES_A_LOAD_OFF_MY_MIND                                      = 11054,  -- Well, that takes a load off my mind.
        I_VE_GOT_PLENTY_OF_SPARK_LEFT_IN                                        = 11055,  -- I've got plenty of spark left in me, though, so don't go getting ahead of yourself! I'll be around whenever you're ready for another bout. Heh heh heh!
        NO_ONE_IS_ALLOWED_TO_MEET_WITH_THE                                      = 11056,  -- No one is allowed to meet with the archduke or the ducal scientists unless it absolutely necessary.
        THE_OFFICIALS_HAVE_BEEN_EXTREMELY_BUSY_MAKING_ARRANGEMENTS              = 11057,  -- The officials have been extremely busy making arrangements for numerous expeditionary forces to be sent to various locations around Quon and Mindartia.
        IF_YOU_HAVE_ANY_BUSINESS_WITH_THE_ARCHDUKE                              = 11058,  -- If you have any business with the archduke or the ducal scientists, please leave your message with us and we will relay it to the proper authorities.
        HOWEVER_WE_CANNOT_GUARANTEE_THAT_YOU_WILL_RECEIVE                       = 11059,  -- However, we cannot guarantee that you will receive a hasty reply.
        THERE_IS_A_MAN_FROM_THE_ALCHEMISTS_GUILD                                = 11060,  -- There is a man from the Alchemists' Guild who has been waiting to speak with the scientists for a number of days.
        I_BELIEVE_HE_IS_STILL_WAITING_SOMEWHERE_NEAR                            = 11061,  -- I believe he is still waiting somewhere near the archduke's quarters. Pour soul...
        DID_YOU_HEAR_SOME_OF_THE_TELEPOINT_CRYSTALS                             = 11062,  -- Did you hear? Some of the Telepoint crystals in Holla, Mea, and Dem have broken into a million pieces!
        SO_THAT_S_WHY_CAPTAIN_WOLFGANG_HAS_BEEN                                 = 11063,  -- So that's why Captain Wolfgang has been on edge lately... But what is really going on at those crags?
        I_SEE_YOU_HAVE_BEGUN_TO_SHOW_SOME                                       = 11064,  -- I see you have begun to show some interest in the strange occurrences that have been taking place in the past few weeks.
        LET_ME_TELL_YOU_A_LITTLE_OF_WHAT                                        = 11065,  -- Let me tell you a little of what I have heard... Recently, the Duchy has been abuzz with strange tales of travelers being drawn into strange whirlpools located in the Valkurm Dunes and on Qufim Island...and never coming back.
        FROM_WHAT_I_GATHER_THE_DUCAL_SCIENTISTS_BELIEVE                         = 11066,  -- From what I gather, the ducal scientists believe this phenomenon has something to do with the shattered Telepoints at the Crags of Holla, Dem, and Mea.
        TO_COLLECT_DATA_A_GROUP_OF_DUCAL_GUARDS                                 = 11067,  -- To collect data, a group of Ducal Guards is to be dispatched any day.
        STRANGE_WHIRLPOOLS_IN_VALKURM_AND_QUFIM_SHATTERED_TELEPOINTS            = 11068,  -- Strange whirlpools in Valkurm and Qufim... Shattered Telepoints... What could it all mean?
        THE_INVESTIGATORY_REPORT_WRITTEN_BY_THE_DUCAL_GUARDS                    = 11069,  -- The investigatory report written by the Ducal Guards mentioned that the whirlpools in Valkurm and Qufim are made up of an unknown substance that they call the Emptiness.
        AND_NOW_THERE_ARE_RUMORS_STATING_THAT_BY                                = 11070,  -- And now there are rumors stating that by jumping into these dark vortexes, people can instantly teleport themselves to the lost island of Tavnazia! I don't know about you, but I am staying right here where it is safe!
        I_VE_HEARD_RUMORS_THAT_A_BRIGHT_LIGHT                                   = 11071,  -- I've heard rumors that a bright light shot out of the sea somewhere to the north of Delkfutt's Tower.
        AN_INVESTIGATORY_PARTY_IS_SCHEDULED_TO_SEARCH_THE                       = 11072,  -- An investigatory party is scheduled to search the area for clues, but they'll have their work cut out for them. The currents in the Sea of Shu'Meyo are unpredictable and violent. Many a captain has lost his ship in those waters.
        DID_YOU_KNOW_THERE_IS_A_MYSTERIOUS_GROUP                                = 11073,  -- Did you know there is a mysterious group of officials in Jeuno known as the Armathrwn Society?
        THE_LAST_TIME_I_TRIED_TELLING_SOME_OF                                   = 11074,  -- The last time I tried telling some of the new recruits about the group, Captain Wolfgang put me on latrine duty for nine and a half weeks!
        YOU_A_SCRUFFY_ADVENTURER_SPOKE_WITH_SIR_NAG                             = 11075,  -- You, a scruffy adventurer, spoke with Sir Nag'molada!?
        DID_YOU_KNOW_THAT_HE_WAS_A_HIGH                                         = 11076,  -- Did you know that he was a high-ranking member of the prestigious Armathrwn Society--the advisors to Archduke Kam'lanaut?
        SIR_NAG_MOLADA_OFTEN_SPEAKS_WITH_COMMON_PEOPLE                          = 11077,  -- Sir Nag'molada often speaks with common people of the Duchy. I even heard that promotions are granted to those who happen to impress him.
        I_WONDER_IF_HE_WILL_EVER_STOP_TO                                        = 11078,  -- I wonder if he will ever stop to speak with me... What would I say?
        YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_RIGHT_SO_YOU_VE                                    = 11079,  -- You're an adventurer, right? So you've probably already heard about the humongous dragon that flew over the western skies.
        AT_FIRST_EVERYBODY_THOUGHT_IT_MIGHT_BE_A                                = 11080,  -- At first everybody thought it might be a stray wyvern, but there are rumors that it was actually one of those ancient wyrms!
        YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_THE_HOODED_OFFICIALS                             = 11081,  -- You want to know about the hooded officials in black robes that sometimes appear in the courtyard?
        THEY_ARE_ALL_MEMBERS_OF_THE_ARMATHRWN_SOCIETY                           = 11082,  -- They are all members of the Armathrwn Society--scientists working for the Duchy. I have heard that there are even quite a few female members.
        WHILE_THE_JEUNO_ARMADA_IS_MAKING_PREPARATIONS_FOR                       = 11083,  -- While the Jeuno Armada is making preparations for battle, it remains the duty of the Ducal Guard to ensure the safety of the citizens of Jeuno.
        DID_YOU_HEAR_THAT_A_SUPER_SECRET_WEAPON                                 = 11084,  -- Did you hear that a super-secret weapon was being loaded onto one of the warships? I wonder what it could be...
        YES_I_OVERHEARD_SOME_OF_THE_OTHER_GUARDS                                = 11085,  -- Yes, I overheard some of the other guards mention that the society's scientists had built a terrifying new battle machine.
        ALRIGHT_AFTER_USING_THAT_CONTRAPTION_ALONG_WITH_THE                     = 11086,  -- Alright! After using that contraption, along with the airships' ultra-powerful mammoth cannons, there won't be enough left of those wyrms to even make dragon burgers!
        THE_JEUNO_ARMADA_IS_READYING_FOR_AN_ATTACK                              = 11087,  -- The Jeuno Armada is readying for an attack on the Wyrmking, Bahamut. However, there is nothing to worry about. Our forces are the strongest, most advanced in all Vana'diel.
        HAVE_YOU_SEEN_A_STRANGE_LOOKING_BOY_OR                                  = 11088,  -- Have you seen a strange-looking boy or girl running about the gardens?
        IF_YOU_HAVE_INFORM_ONE_OF_THE_DUCAL                                     = 11089,  -- If you have, inform one of the Ducal Guards. There are currently warrrrants out for both of their arrrrests.
        THEIR_CAPTURE_IS_CRUCIAL_TO_THE_SAFETY_OF                               = 11090,  -- Their capture is crucial to the safety of not just Jeuno, but of all Vana'diel. You and your fellow adventurers' assistance in the matter is greatly appreciated.
        MEMBERS_OF_THE_ARMATHRWN_SOCIETY_ARE_TO_ACCOMPANY                       = 11091,  -- Members of the Armathrwn Society are to accompany the armada on its mission. It is said that the society's technological advancements are what built this city and made it what it is today.
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL_IS_SUPPOSEDLY_LEADING_THE_MISSION                       = 11092,  -- Lady Esha'ntarl is supposedly leading the mission against Bahamut. With such a skilled commander at the armada's helm, there isn't anything in Vana'diel that can stop the Duchy!
        I_KNOW_YOU_MAY_CONSIDER_YOUR_NATION_A                                   = 11093,  -- I know you may consider your nation a powerful force in Vana'diel, but Jeuno is the only nation with the resources to defeat the Wyrmking. Don't you forget it.
        ONE_OF_THE_ARMADA_WARSHIPS_IS_MISSING_WITH                              = 11094,  -- One of the armada warships is missing! With all the tightened security, how could anyone have pulled off a feat as grand as stealing an airship!?
        WHILE_THE_JEUNO_ARMADA_IS_CONDUCTING_ITS_MISSION                        = 11095,  -- While the Jeuno Armada is conducting its mission in the skies, it remains the duty of the Ducal Guard to ensure the safety of the citizens of Jeuno.
        DID_YOU_FIND_OUT_ANYTHING_MORE_ABOUT_THE                                = 11096,  -- Did you find out anything more about the super-secret weapon the armada took with them?
        NO_HOWEVER_I_DID_HEAR_THAT_THE_DEVICE                                   = 11097,  -- No... However, I did hear that the device dealt a severe blow to the mighty Wyrmking during the assault.
        WOWZIE_IF_I_HAD_AN_ULTRA_SPIFFY_CONTRAPTION                             = 11098,  -- Wowzie! If I had an ultra-spiffy contraption like that, I'd be eating roast dragon burgers every night!
        THE_LATEST_REPORTS_STATE_THE_RECENT_ARMADA_MISSION                      = 11099,  -- The latest reports state the recent armada mission was a success. However, it did not completely stop the Wyrmking and his minions. It is rumored that the fleet will launch its second attack once the current repairs on the warships are completed.
        IF_YOU_HAVE_ANY_INFORMATION_ON_THE_WHEREABOUTS                          = 11100,  -- If you have any information on the whereabouts of the girl the Duchy was searching for, I am sorry, but the warrant for her arrest has been dropped.
        THE_DUCAL_GUARD_RECENTLY_RECEIVED_NEWS_OF_HER                           = 11101,  -- The Ducal Guard recently received news of her death...
        EVEN_WITH_THE_TECHNOLOGY_OF_THE_ARMATHRWN_SOCIETY                       = 11102,  -- Even with the technology of the Armathrwn Society on our side, the armada was unable to completely defeat the Wyrmking and his army. Perhaps we underestimated their power...
        IN_ITS_FIRST_WAVE_OF_ATTACKS_THE_ARMADA                                 = 11103,  -- In its first wave of attacks, the armada was successful in dealing a large amount of damage to Bahamut. The Wyrmking will not stand a chance against the second wave.
        SIGH_I_REQUESTED_A_TRANSFER_FROM_THE_DUCAL                              = 11104,  -- <Sigh> I requested a transfer from the Ducal Guard to the armada crew, but I was turned down...
        WHY_DO_I_HAVE_TO_STAND_AROUND_THE                                       = 11105,  -- Why do I have to stand around the gardens while everyone else is having all the fun? Look at these biceps! I could take out a wyrm with one blow! Well...maybe two blows.
        WE_WERE_BEGINNING_TO_WONDER_WHEN_YOU_WOULD                              = 11106,  -- We were beginning to wonder when you would arrive, %.
        THE_DUKE_VICARIOUS_IS_MEETING_A_MESSENGER_FROM                          = 11107,  -- The duke vicarious is meeting a messenger from the East as we speak. When she is finished, you shall be next. Until then, you shall be kept in custody.
        I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_THE_ABSENCE_OF_GRAND_DUKE                               = 11108,  -- I apologize for the absence of Grand Duke Kam'lanaut. I, Esha'ntarl, shall serve in his stead.
        I_HEAR_THAT_YOU_HAVE_COME_FROM_THE                                      = 11109,  -- I hear that you have come from the Eastern Empire to ask something of our nation. State your name and your request.
        I_AM_TENZEN_BORN_AND_RAISED_IN_THE                                      = 11110,  -- ...I am Tenzen. Born and raised in the Far East, I serve as a samurai under the mighty dynasty.
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL_MAY_I_ASK_WHY_MY                                        = 11111,  -- Lady Esha'ntarl, may I ask why my audience was not met by the duke himself?
        THE_GRAND_DUKE_HAS_BEEN_OVERWHELMED_WITH_HIS                            = 11112,  -- [Since the revival of the Shadow Lord/Even after the defeat of the Shadow Lord], the grand duke has been overwhelmed with his duties to the people of this land.
        HOWEVER_YOU_NEED_NOT_WORRY_I_WILL_TAKE                                  = 11113,  -- However, you need not worry. I will take the responsibility of relaying your words directly to Lord Kam'lanaut.
        THESE_TWO_SHALL_BE_WITNESS_TO_THAT                                      = 11114,  -- These two shall be witness to that.
        ID_11115                                                                = 11115,  -- ...
        WHILE_SHORT_MY_MESSAGE_IS_NOT_A_SIMPLE                                  = 11116,  -- While short, my message is not a simple one. It is critical that the duke fully understands the grave nature of the situation that lies before us.
        WHAT_I_AM_ABOUT_TO_SAY_DOES_NOT                                         = 11117,  -- What I am about to say does not only affect my homeland, but the countries to the south and west, as well as this fair land.
        THE_EMPTINESS_IS_CLOSING_IN_IT_HAS_ALREADY                              = 11118,  -- The Emptiness is closing in. It has already appeared in the far reaches of the Eastern Empire. I can assume that the same is true of the outlying areas in the southern and western lands.
        THE_PHENOMENON_STARTED_SMALL_BUT_IN_RECENT_MONTHS                       = 11119,  -- The phenomenon started small, but in recent months it has begun to grow. Like sap oozes slowly from a tree, the Emptiness spreads across my country, swallowing whole the hills and forests.
        AS_IT_APPROACHES_THE_CHILDREN_BEGIN_TO_DREAM                            = 11120,  -- As it approaches, the children begin to dream. When it arrives, it is not long before the adults, too, begin to dream.
        THE_DREAM_IS_ALWAYS_THE_SAME_IT_TELLS                                   = 11121,  -- The dream is always the same... It tells us...the Keeper of the Apocalypse will soon appear, and bring with him the end of Vana'diel.
        THE_KEEPER_OF_THE_APOCALYPSE_A_FRIGHTENING_NAME                         = 11122,  -- The Keeper of the Apocalypse... A frightening name, is it not?
        YOUR_REPORT_OF_THIS_DARKNESS_THIS_EMPTINESS_IT                          = 11123,  -- Your report of this darkness--this Emptiness--it is not news to us. In recent weeks, there have been reports of similar phenomena occurring in the areas around Jeuno.
        HOWEVER_THESE_REPORTS_STATE_THAT_THE_EMPTINESS_AS                       = 11124,  -- However, these reports state that the Emptiness, as you call it, is localized. That is why we have chosen to withhold this information from the public until it can be further researched. If it is true that the Emptiness has begun to spread, though, an immediate investigation may be necessary.
        SHALL_THE_DUCHY_PREPARE_A_TEAM                                          = 11125,  -- Shall the Duchy prepare a team?
        YOU_DO_NOT_KNOW_WHY_THE_EMPTINESS_HAS                                   = 11126,  -- ... You...do not know why the Emptiness has appeared?
        UNFORTUNATELY_OUR_SCIENTISTS_HAVE_NOT_YET_COME_TO                       = 11127,  -- Unfortunately, our scientists have not yet come to any concrete conclusions. If your empire has any definite data, we would be delighted to hear it.
        ARE_YOU_SUGGESTING_THAT_THE_CAUSE_OF_THE                                = 11128,  -- Are you suggesting that the cause of the Emptiness may be found in my land? Do not tell me that you are unaware that the five shards of legend rest here!
        DO_NOT_TELL_ME_THAT_YOU_ARE_UNAWARE                                     = 11129,  -- Do not tell me that you are unaware that it is the power of the five shards that protects Vana'diel from the Emptiness!
        TENZEN_OF_THE_EAST_YOU_ARE_VERY_STRAIGHTFORWARD                         = 11130,  -- Tenzen of the East... You are very straightforward with your accusations.
        LET_ME_SEE_YOU_FEEL_THAT_JEUNO_IS                                       = 11131,  -- Let me see... You feel that Jeuno is the cause of the Emptiness's growth. You feel that our attempts to harness the power of the crystals have resulted in the spread of the darkness, am I correct?
        WELL_I_AM_SORRY_TO_SAY_THAT_YOU                                         = 11132,  -- Well, I am sorry to say that you are quite mistaken. Jeuno is fully aware of the power that the crystals radiate forth.
        THE_FIVE_SHARDS_THE_MOTHERCRYSTALS_ARE_WHAT_SUPPORT                     = 11133,  -- The five shards--the mothercrystals--are what support our world.
        WE_THE_DUCHY_HAVE_TAKEN_IT_UPON_OURSELVES                               = 11134,  -- We, the Duchy, have taken it upon ourselves to inherit the will of the ancients and protect the Zilartian ruins and the crystals they hold.
        WE_HAVE_KEPT_THIS_INFORMATION_FROM_THE_NATIONS                          = 11135,  -- We have kept this information from the nations of Bastok, Windurst, and San d'Oria to shield the mothercrystals from those who may wish to wrongly use their power for personal gain.
        I_SEE_THAT_THE_EASTERN_EMPIRE_HAS_LEARNED                               = 11136,  -- I see that the Eastern Empire has learned of the crystals' existence, and therefore we can no longer trust you, either.
        JEUNO_CANNOT_ALLOW_THE_POWER_OF_THE_MOTHERCRYSTALS                      = 11137,  -- Jeuno cannot allow the power of the mothercrystals to fall into the hands of those who may exploit it.
        MY_COUNTRY_S_ONLY_WISH_IS_TO_PREVENT                                    = 11138,  -- My country's only wish is to prevent the Emptiness from taking away any more than it already has!
        SEEING_WITH_YOUR_OWN_EYES_THE_DARKNESS_DRAIN                            = 11139,  -- Seeing, with your own eyes, the darkness drain the life from your homeland... I can understand why you may not agree with our nation's stance.
        VERY_WELL_I_CAN_TELL_YOU_ONE_THING                                      = 11140,  -- Very well. I can tell you one thing. The Duchy is currently in search of a boy. This boy is thought to be connected in some way to the Emptiness.
        EVEN_THOUGH_HE_IS_NOT_ONE_OF_US                                         = 11141,  -- Even though he is not one of us, he has already found a way into three of the Zilartian ruins, the Emptiness following in his path.
        WE_HERE_BELIEVE_THAT_THIS_BOY_IS_THE                                    = 11142,  -- We here believe that this boy is the Keeper of the Apocalypse of which you speak.
        A_BOY_COULD_HE_BE_A_MESSENGER_FROM                                      = 11143,  -- A boy? Could he be a messenger from another nation?
        THAT_WE_DO_NOT_KNOW_HOWEVER                                             = 11144,  -- That we do not know. However...
        WOLFGANG_SHOW_THE_ADVENTURER_IN                                         = 11145,  -- Wolfgang. Show the adventurer in.
        THIS_ADVENTURER_WAS_WITH_THE_BOY_WHEN_HE                                = 11146,  -- This adventurer was with the boy when he appeared near the mothercrystals. He/She] hails from the nation of [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst].
        WHAT_COULD_BE_CONSPIRING                                                = 11147,  -- [San d'Oria/The Republic/The Federation]! What could [the king/the president/those mages] be conspiring!?
        OF_COURSE_HAS_DENIED_ALL_TIES_TO_THE                                    = 11148,  -- Of course, [the Kingdom/Bastok/Windurst] has denied all ties to the boy.
        AS_HAS_THIS_ADVENTURER                                                  = 11149,  -- As has this adventurer.
        HOWEVER_IF_WE_LEARN_THAT_IS_BEHIND_THIS                                 = 11150,  -- However, if we learn that [San d'Oria/the Republic/the Federation] is behind this threat to the mothercrystals and the well-being of all those residing on Vana'diel...
        WHETHER_ALLIES_OR_NOT_JEUNO_WILL_BE_FORCED                              = 11151,  -- Whether allies or not, Jeuno will be forced to take action against the nation. We will destroy them.
        BUT_THIS_IS_STILL_NOTHING_MORE_THAN_SPECULATION                         = 11152,  -- But this is still nothing more than speculation. If we had the time to conduct a proper investigation, it would be the first thing we did. Unfortunately, time is one luxury we do not have.
        AND_THAT_IS_WHY_WE_MUST_CAPTURE_THE                                     = 11153,  -- And that is why we must capture the boy immediately to learn of what he knows...
        EXACTLY_AND_THAT_IS_WHY_I_OFFER_YOU                                     = 11154,  -- Exactly. And that is why I offer you a chance--a chance to prove your country's true intents by joining this battle to save your nation--no, all of Vana'diel.
        ADVENTURER_TRAVEL_TO_THE_FOURTH_CRYSTAL_AND_WAIT                        = 11155,  -- Adventurer. Travel to the fourth crystal and wait for the boy. When he arrives, capture him and bring him here.
        UNLIKE_THE_FIRST_THREE_CRYSTALS_THE_FOURTH_LIES                         = 11156,  -- Unlike the first three crystals, the fourth lies deep beneath Vana'diel's surface, somewhere below the glaciers of the Northlands.
        THIRTY_YEARS_AGO_AN_ALLIED_EXPEDITION_VISITED_THE                       = 11157,  -- Thirty years ago, an allied expedition visited the Northlands. If you could find one of the original members, you may be able to obtain some valuable information.
        FRANCMAGE_M_MISTALLE_OF_THE_KNIGHTS_MISTALLE_IN                         = 11158,  -- Francmage M Mistalle, of the Knights Mistalle in San d'Oria... Iru-Kuiru, from the Rhinostery in Windurst... Mythril Musketeer captain, Ulrich, from Bastok...
        I_HAVE_HEARD_NEWS_THAT_THE_CRIMINAL_ACCUSED                             = 11159,  -- I have heard news that the criminal accused of destroying the Telepoints was captured and taken into custody.
        HOWEVER_WHEN_QUESTIONED_HE_SHE_SAID_SHE_HAD                             = 11160,  -- However, when questioned, he/she] said she had nothing to do with the incidents. To prove his/her] innocence, the Duchy has ordered the scoundrel to travel to the nations of Bastok, Windurst, and San d'Oria and gather information that will clear his/her] name.
        WHAT_IS_THIS_YOU_SAY_YOU_HAVE_BUSINESS                                  = 11161,  -- What is this? You say you have business with the captain?
        AH_I_WAS_LOOKING_FOR_YOU                                                = 11162,  -- Ah, %. I was looking for you.
        ESHA_NTARL_DUKE_VICARIOUS_WOULD_LIKE_TO_HEAR                            = 11163,  -- Esha'ntarl, duke vicarious, would like to hear your account of what transpired in the Northlands.
        WHAT_IS_THIS_ENVELOPE                                                   = 11164,  -- ...? What is this envelope?
        FROM_DOCTOR_MONBERAUX_WHY_WOULD_HE                                      = 11165,  -- From Doctor Monberaux? Why would he...?
        HOWEVER_FIRST_THINGS_FIRST_FOLLOW_ME                                    = 11166,  -- However, first things first. Follow me.
        AH_WELCOME_BACK_ADVENTURER                                              = 11167,  -- Ah, welcome back, adventurer.
        I_SEE_THAT_YOU_WERE_UNSUCCESSFUL_IN_PROTECTING                          = 11168,  -- I see that you were unsuccessful in protecting the fourth crystal.
        AND_NOW_IT_IS_LOOKING_MORE_AND_MORE                                     = 11169,  -- And now it is looking more and more like you are the one who is leading the boy...
        RELAX_ADVENTURER_I_AM_NOT_BLAMING_YOU_FOR                               = 11170,  -- Relax, adventurer. I am not blaming you for anything.
        NAG_MOLADA_KEPT_THE_SECRET_OF_THE_AMULET                                = 11171,  -- Nag'molada kept the secret of the amulet to himself.
        IT_IS_HIS_FOOLISHNESS_THAT_ACTED_AS_A                                   = 11172,  -- It is his foolishness that acted as a catalyst for what occurred in the Northlands.
        AND_NOW_THAT_WE_KNOW_THE_TRUE_IDENTITY                                  = 11173,  -- And now that we know the true identity of the boy, there is no reason to further suspect your nation's involvement. I apologize for not trusting you.
        HOWEVER_NOW_WE_MUST_PUT_ASIDE_OUR_MISUNDERSTANDINGS                     = 11174,  -- However, now we must put aside our misunderstandings and unite to save our world from being destroyed. Will you help us protect the mothercrystals?
        JOIN_FORCES_WITH_JEUNO_YES_NO                                           = 11175,  -- Join forces with Jeuno? Yes. No.
        WE_HAVE_CAUSED_YOU_MUCH_SUFFERING_AND_I                                 = 11176,  -- We have caused you much suffering, and I understand your anger. On behalf of the Duchy I ask for your forgiveness.
        ID_11177                                                                = 11177,  -- %...
        IN_THE_PRESENCE_OF_THE_FOURTH_CRYSTAL_I                                 = 11178,  -- In the presence of the fourth crystal, I have learned that a strange occurrence took place.
        IS_IT_TRUE_THAT_THE_GIRL_YOU_TOOK                                       = 11179,  -- Is it true that the girl you took with you actually helped Selh'teus and thwarted the plans of our Nag'molada?
        IT_IS_EXTREMELY_IMPORTANT_THAT_YOU_DO_NOT                               = 11180,  -- It is extremely important that you do not withhold information from us.
        IS_IT_TRUE_YES_NO                                                       = 11181,  -- Is it true? Yes. No.
        I_SEE_THE_DUCHY_IS_CURRENTLY_SEARCHING_FOR                              = 11182,  -- I see... The Duchy is currently searching for that girl.
        WE_DO_NOT_WISH_TO_PUNISH_HER_WE                                         = 11183,  -- We do not wish to punish her. We feel that she may be in grave danger. We must find her so we can protect her.
        THE_FIRST_THREAT_TO_HER_WILL_BE_NAG                                     = 11184,  -- The first threat to her will be Nag'molada. He is already attempting to make it seem as if the fall of the fourth crystal was the girl's fault.
        IF_HE_FINDS_HER_HE_WILL_MORE_THAN                                       = 11185,  -- If he finds her, he will more than likely poison her mind, preventing her from speaking of anything that may harm his plan.
        THE_SECOND_THREAT_WILL_BE_THE_BOY_SELH                                  = 11186,  -- The second threat will be the boy, Selh'teus. His next destination will most surely be the fifth and final crystal.
        HOWEVER_THIS_CRYSTAL_LIES_DEEP_BENEATH_THE_SEA                          = 11187,  -- However, this crystal lies deep beneath the sea, and the only one who knows how to reach it is the girl.
        FINALLY_THE_THIRD_THREAT_WILL_CONSIST_OF_ASSASSINS                      = 11188,  -- Finally, the third threat will consist of assassins from the south.
        YOU_MAY_HAVE_ALREADY_HEARD_THE_RUMORS_OF                                = 11189,  -- You may have already heard the rumors of the Mithran sin hunters who have crossed the southern seas to try the theologians of Tavnazia.
        THESE_HUNTERS_WILL_NOT_GIVE_UP_UNTIL_THEY                               = 11190,  -- These hunters will not give up until they have punished all those they seek.
        AND_THAT_IS_WHY_WE_NEED_YOUR_HELP                                       = 11191,  -- And that is why we need your help, %.
        IF_YOU_FIND_THE_GIRL_BRING_HER_HERE                                     = 11192,  -- If you find the girl, bring her here. No harm will be brought to her. I swear on the name of the Goddess.
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL                                                         = 11193,  -- Lady Esha'ntarl!
        DID_YOU_TELL_THEM_EVERYTHING_THAT_HAPPENED_IN                           = 11194,  -- %. Did you tell them everything that happened in the Northlands?
        MY_PLAN_WAS_FLAWLESS_IF_IT_WASN_T                                       = 11195,  -- My plan was flawless! If it wasn't for that despicable girl, Prishe, I would have captured Selh'teus, and this whole ordeal would be solved!
        THAT_GIRL_HEARD_THE_WHISPER_OF_SELH_TEUS                                = 11196,  -- That girl heard the whisper of Selh'teus's soul, sang the Memoria de la S^tona, and helped him escape!
        THE_TESTAMENT_OF_AFFINITY_SHE_POSSESSES_IT_CONNECTS                     = 11197,  -- The testament of affinity she possesses--it connects the hearts and souls of men. Selh'teus has been using that to control her!
        ID_11198                                                                = 11198,  -- ...
        BUT_NOW_WE_HAVE_THE_CHANCE_TO_FIND                                      = 11199,  -- But now we have the chance to find out his true intentions.
        IF_WE_CAN_CAPTURE_THE_GIRL_WE_CAN                                       = 11200,  -- If we can capture the girl, we can use her to tap into Selh'teus's mind. We can learn if he truly arrived to save Al'Taieu!
        YOU_MISERABLE_MAN_ARE_YOU_SAYING_SELH_TEUS                              = 11201,  -- You miserable man! Are you saying Selh'teus does not know that our crusade ended long ago?
        YOU_FOOL_ARE_YOU_SAYING_SELH_TEUS_DOES                                  = 11202,  -- You fool! Are you saying Selh'teus does not know that the celestial capital was destroyed long ago?
        PERHAPS_IT_IS_WE_WHO_DO_NOT_KNOW                                        = 11203,  -- Perhaps it is we who do not know the true outcome of the crusade or the true fate of our capital!
        I_PROPOSE_THAT_AN_EXPEDITION_BE_SENT_TO                                 = 11204,  -- I propose that an expedition be sent to Al'Taieu.
        THERE_WE_MAY_FIND_THE_ANSWERS_TO_WHY                                    = 11205,  -- There we may find the answers to why Selh'teus survived all the centuries, and why he continues to poison the mothercrystals.
        AND_THAT_IS_WHY_WE_MUST_FIRST_INVESTIGATE                               = 11206,  -- And that is why we must first investigate the line leading to the fifth crystal.
        PLEASE_GRANT_ME_ACCESS_TO_THE_CRYSTAL_TERMINAL                          = 11207,  -- Please, grant me access to the Crystal Terminal!
        I_UNDERSTAND_WHY_YOU_FEEL_AN_EXPEDITION_TO                              = 11208,  -- ... I understand why you feel an expedition to Al'Taieu is necessary.
        HOWEVER                                                                 = 11209,  -- However...
        HAS_ALREADY_MADE_A_DECISION_ON_THIS_MATTER                              = 11210,  -- [The Armathrwn Society/Kam'lanaut] has already made a decision on this matter. I seem to recall that you have been given orders to research the Moblin city that was discovered near Bastok.
        ALL_AFFAIRS_CONCERNING_SELH_TEUS_HAVE_BEEN_LEFT                         = 11211,  -- All affairs concerning Selh'teus have been left to Esha'ntarl. You are not to interfere.
        BUT_LADY_ESHA_NTARL_HAS_BEEN_GIVEN_THE                                  = 11212,  -- But, Lady Esha'ntarl has been given the assignment of Bahamut.
        SELH_TEUS_IS_A_MUCH_GRAVER_PROBLEM_THAN                                 = 11213,  -- Selh'teus is a much graver problem than you can imagine. I do not think...
        YES_YOU_DO_NOT_THINK_DID_YOU_REALLY                                     = 11214,  -- Yes, you do not think! Did you really believe attacking the boy with the Eye of Altana would defeat him!?
        YOUR_IMPUDENCE_IS_THE_CAUSE_OF_ALL_OUR                                  = 11215,  -- Your impudence is the cause of all our troubles!
        BUT                                                                     = 11216,  -- But...
        NAG_MOLADA_DO_NOT_MISUNDERSTAND_US_NOT_INTEND                           = 11217,  -- Nag'molada, do not misunderstand us. [The society does/Kam'lanaut does] not intend to pry at your faults.
        THE_REASON_WE_HAVE_ENTRUSTED_YOU_WITH_THE                               = 11218,  -- The reason we have entrusted you with the Moblin investigation is because your excellent Kuluu powers of negotiation are vital for the success of the mission.
        BUT_LADY_ESHA_NTARL_YOU_DO_NOT_REALIZE                                  = 11219,  -- But Lady Esha'ntarl! You do not realize how powerful the boy has become...
        NOW_WITH_THE_EYE_GONE_AND_THE_PATH                                      = 11220,  -- Now with the Eye gone and the path to the fifth crystal sealed, how do you plan on dealing with him!?
        I_DON_T_THINK_YOU_EVEN_HAVE_A                                           = 11221,  -- I don't think you even have a plan!
        VERY_WELL_LET_ME_INFORM_YOU_OF_HOW                                      = 11222,  -- Very well, let me inform you of how we plan to stop Selh'teus.
        WE_CAN_DRAW_HIM_FORTH_WITHOUT_TRAVELING_TO                              = 11223,  -- We can draw him forth without traveling to the fifth crystal. We can seal him without your precious Eye of Altana.
        H_HOW                                                                   = 11224,  -- H-how...!?
        YOU_CAN_HEAR_ME_CAN_YOU_NOT_SELH                                        = 11225,  -- You can hear me, can you not...Selh'teus?
        IT_IS_I_WHO_POSSESS_THE_OTHER_AMULET                                    = 11226,  -- It is I who possess the other amulet you seek.
        I_AM_WAITING_SELH_TEUS_COME_AND_FULFILL                                 = 11227,  -- I am waiting, Selh'teus! Come and fulfill the pact!
        HERE_TAKE_THIS_ENVELOPE_BACK_TO_THE_DOCTOR                              = 11228,  -- Here, take this envelope back to the doctor. It does not belong to me.
        BUT_WHY_WOULD_HE_TRY_TO                                                 = 11229,  -- But why would he try to...?
        NOT_BUT_A_FEW_MOMENTS_AGO_SIR_NAG                                       = 11230,  -- Not but a few moments ago, Sir Nag'molada passed by this station. However, he did not seem himself. I wonder if something is wrong...
        EVEN_CAPTAIN_WOLFGANG_HAS_BEEN_LOOKING_DISTURBED_SINCE                  = 11231,  -- Even Captain Wolfgang has been looking disturbed since he received that envelope. What ever could be going on?
        CURRENTLY_ONLY_PLAYERS_ABOVE_LEVEL_49_CAN_USE                           = 11232,  -- Currently, only players above level 49 can use the Ru'Lude Gardens auction house. Thank you for your cooperation.
        CURRENTLY_ONLY_PLAYERS_BETWEEN_LEVELS_35_AND_55                         = 11233,  -- Currently, only players between levels 35 and 55 can use the Upper Jeuno auction service. Thank you for your cooperation.
        CURRENTLY_ONLY_PLAYERS_BETWEEN_LEVELS_20_AND_40                         = 11234,  -- Currently, only players between levels 20 and 40 can use the Lower Jeuno auction house. Thank you for your cooperation.
        CURRENTLY_ONLY_PLAYERS_BELOW_LEVEL_26_CAN_USE                           = 11235,  -- Currently, only players below level 26 can use the Port Jeuno auction service. Thank you for your cooperation.
        YOU_HEAR_A_MYSTERIOUS_FLOATING_VOICE_BRING_FORTH                        = 11236,  -- You hear a mysterious, floating voice: Bring forth the %...
        YOU_DO_NOT_MEET_THE_REQUIREMENTS                                        = 11237,  -- You do not meet the requirements.
        THE_TIME_AND_DESTINATION_FOR_YOUR_FORAY_INTO                            = 11238,  -- The time and destination for your foray into Dynamis will be recorded on your %. === Destination: Dynamis - [Dummy/San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst/Jeuno/Beaucedine/Xarcabard/Valkurm/Buburimu/Qufim/Tavnazia] ===
        RECORD_THE_TIME_AND_DESTINATION_PROCEED_NOT_YET                         = 11239,  -- Record the time and destination? Proceed. Not yet. Entering Dynamis - [Dummy/San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst/Jeuno/Beaucedine/Xarcabard/Valkurm/Buburimu/Qufim/Tavnazia]. Reentering Dynamis - [Dummy/San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst/Jeuno/Beaucedine/Xarcabard/Valkurm/Buburimu/Qufim/Tavnazia]. Battles in Dynamis - [Dummy/San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst/Jeuno/Beaucedine/Xarcabard/Valkurm/Buburimu/Qufim/Tavnazia].
        CONNECTING_WITH_SERVER_PLEASE_WAIT                                      = 11240,  -- Connecting with server. Please wait.
        UNABLE_TO_CONNECT                                                       = 11241,  -- Unable to connect.
