        IT_IS_A_PITY_INDEED                                                     = 11536,  -- It is a pity, indeed.
        THIS_DAY_HAS_COME_FAR_TOO_SOON_FOR                                      = 11537,  -- This day has come far too soon for my liking.
        HOWEVER_YOU_ARE_A_MASTER_OF_THE_NINJA                                   = 11538,  -- However, you are a master of the ninja trade. I concede that you will make a fitting wielder of the %.
        TAKE_THIS_BLADE_AS_YOUR_OWN_TRAVEL_FAR                                  = 11539,  -- Take this blade as your own. Travel far down the path of the ninja.
        I_WILL_BE_WATCHING_YOU_FROM_THE_SHADOWS                                 = 11540,  -- I will be watching you from the shadows...
        ID_11541                                                                = 11541,  -- ...
        A_FINE_MASTER                                                           = 11542,  -- A fine master...
        MY_KEEN_EDGE_IS_NOW_YOURS_TO_WIELD                                      = 11543,  -- My keen edge is now yours to wield. A sharpness said to make even demons wail...
        THIS_DAY_HAS_FINALLY_COME                                               = 11544,  -- ... This day has finally come.
        I_AM_TO_BE_RELEASED_TO_THIS_WORLD                                       = 11545,  -- I am to be released to this world for the first time in an age. Is this reason to celebrate, or despair...?
        IN_ANY_EVENT                                                            = 11546,  -- In any event...
        WHAT_IS_GOING_ON_HERE                                                   = 11547,  -- What is going on here?
        AH_MY_SUCCESSOR_HAS_COME                                                = 11548,  -- Ah, my successor has come.
        I_SOUGHT_TO_MASTER_THE_WAY_OF_THE                                       = 11549,  -- I sought to master the way of the samurai, and traveled to the Far East for training. By the time I had gained the % and returned to my home, the Great War had begun.
        WHEN_I_THINK_ON_IT_MY_LIFE_HAS                                          = 11550,  -- When I think on it, my life has been a long road of trials. But to see the arrival of my successor makes me feel that all has not been in vain.
        YOU_HAVE_MY_GRATITUDE_FAREWELL                                          = 11551,  -- You have my gratitude. Farewell, %...
        ID_11552                                                                = 11552,  -- ...
        IT_HAS_BEEN_A_HARD_PATH_TO_REACH                                        = 11553,  -- It has been a hard path to reach this point.
        BUT_YOUR_JOURNEY_IN_THE_WAY_OF_THE                                      = 11554,  -- But your journey in the way of the samurai has just begun. You have yet to attain perfection. Let us continue your training...
        AT_LONG_LAST_YOU_HAVE_ARRIVED                                           = 11555,  -- ... At long last, you have arrived.
        I_WAS_NOT_CONVINCED_YOU_WERE_SERIOUS_ABOUT                              = 11556,  -- I was not convinced you were serious about completing this trial...
        YOU_HAVE_PROVEN_ME_WRONG                                                = 11557,  -- You have proven me wrong...
        I_HAVE_HEARD_OF_YOUR_COMING                                             = 11558,  -- I have heard of your coming.
        YOU_ARE_TO_BE_THE_NEW_MASTER_OF                                         = 11559,  -- You are to be the new master of this hammer of war?
        EVERY_TIME_IS_REBORN_IT_GAINS_A_NEW                                     = 11560,  -- Every time % is reborn it gains a new wielder, who ultimately must pass it on to a successor. I have swung this hammer for more than eight hundred years. I never wished to part with it.
        HOWEVER_THERE_IS_LITTLE_MEANING_IN_ME_KEEPING                           = 11561,  -- However, there is little meaning in me keeping it now. If you will wield this weapon for a just cause, I hand its power over to you.
        NOW_TAKE_THE_HAMMER_AND_GO_JUST_BE                                      = 11562,  -- Now, take the hammer and go! Just be careful with how you handle it. Do not let its might crush you as well...
        ID_11563                                                                = 11563,  -- ...
        MY_MIGHT_IS_YOURS_TO_WIELD                                              = 11564,  -- My might is yours to wield.
        GO_FORTH_AND_EXPERIENCE_THE_DESTRUCTIVE_POWER_THAT                      = 11565,  -- Go forth and experience the destructive power that laid low the Earth Serpent...
        SO_YOU_HAVE_FOUND_ME                                                    = 11566,  -- ... So, you have found me.
        I_MUST_GIVE_YOU_MY_THANKS_I_HAVE                                        = 11567,  -- I must give you my thanks. I have been freed from the hell of Dynamis and can regain my true power once again.
        AND_NOW                                                                 = 11568,  -- And now...
        HWAAH                                                                   = 11569,  -- Hwaah!
        JUST_WHEN_I_THOUGHT_I_HAD_FINALLY_RETURNED                              = 11570,  -- Just when I thought I had finally returned to this world, I find you standing here, ready to snatch my precious staff away.
        WELL_IT_S_FOR_THE_BEST_I_SUPPOSE                                        = 11571,  -- Well, it's for the best, I suppose. In my current state, % is nothing more than an ornament, its power going to waste.
        I_ENTRUST_THIS_STAFF_TO_YOU_TAKE_UP                                     = 11572,  -- I entrust this staff to you! Take up %, %, and bind it to you in a contract of blood!
        I_TAKE_MY_LEAVE_OF_YOU_NOW_I                                            = 11573,  -- I take my leave of you now. I only wish that I was able to stay a little longer...
        ID_11574                                                                = 11574,  -- ...
        I_AM_YOURS_TO_WIELD                                                     = 11575,  -- I am yours to wield.
        BUT_YOU_ARE_NOT_YET_MY_MASTER_BY                                        = 11576,  -- But you are not yet my master. By watching your actions from this time onwards, I will decide if you are worthy of the title...
        YOU_HAVE_DISCOVERED_MY_RESTING_PLACE                                    = 11577,  -- ... You have discovered my resting place.
        THE_PRISON_OF_SOULS_HAS_LET_LOOSE_ITS                                   = 11578,  -- The prison of souls has let loose its shackles, and I am free to loose arrows in this world once more. My thanks.
        AH_ONE_MORE_TEST_OF_YOUR_PATIENCE                                       = 11579,  -- Ah, one more test of your patience...
        WHERE_IS_THIS_PLACE                                                     = 11580,  -- Where is this place?
        OF_COURSE_HOW_COULD_I_FORGET_I_AM                                       = 11581,  -- Of course. How could I forget. I am Ghebben. I was entrusted with this bow by a warrior of the Far East.
        YOUR_HANDS_TELL_ME_THAT_YOUR_SKILL_IN                                   = 11582,  -- Your hands tell me that your skill in archery is far from ordinary. % will fit snugly into your sure grasp.
        HOWEVER_THIS_BOW_BELONGS_TO_SIR_NASU_THE                                = 11583,  -- However, this bow belongs to Sir Nasu, the warrior of whom I spoke. You must remember that you are merely its keeper for a time.
        FAREWELL                                                                = 11584,  -- Farewell...
        ID_11585                                                                = 11585,  -- ...
        IT_IS_AN_HONOR_TO_BE_OWNED_BY                                           = 11586,  -- It is an honor to be owned by a just master. Sir Ghebben was a truly splendid archer.
        YOU_ARE_NOW_THE_ONE_TO_DRAW_ME                                          = 11587,  -- You are now the one to draw me in battle. I will be at your side on any road you choose to travel, along with the destructive power of my arrows.
        WE_FINALLY_MEET                                                         = 11588,  -- ... We finally meet.
        I_AM_NOW_FREE_FROM_THE_PIT_OF                                           = 11589,  -- I am now free from the pit of Dynamis to spit fire in this world once again.
        BUT_I_MUST_ASK_YOU_TO_WAIT_BEFORE                                       = 11590,  -- But I must ask you to wait before taking me into your possession...
        WHY_D_YOU_HAVE_TO_GO_AND_WAKE                                           = 11591,  -- Why'd you have to go and wake me up? I was having the most relaxing sleep. Oh, this place looks familiar...
        HM_YOU_THINK_YOU_RE_THE_ONE_WHO                                         = 11592,  -- Hm? You think you're the one who's going to take up my gun?
        YOU_DO_SEEM_TO_HAVE_A_FAIR_EYE                                          = 11593,  -- You do seem to have a fair eye for marksmanship. And % would look perfect nestled in the crook of your arm...
        WELL_I_HAVE_NO_MORE_USE_FOR_THIS                                        = 11594,  -- Well, I have no more use for this weapon, so I guess you can have it. But there is one thing I want you to remember.
        THIS_GUN_IS_A_FEARSOME_WEAPON_THAT_UNLEASHES                            = 11595,  -- This gun is a fearsome weapon that unleashes a blast upon your enemies many thousands of times greater in strength than the tiny effort it takes you to pull the trigger. Needless to say, be careful who you aim it at...
        ID_11596                                                                = 11596,  -- ...
        A_WEAPON_HAS_NO_WILL_OF_ITS_OWN                                         = 11597,  -- A weapon has no will of its own. But it was made for a purpose.
        TAKE_ME_TO_A_NEW_BATTLEFIELD_A_NEW                                      = 11598,  -- Take me to a new battlefield, a new arena for the hunt...
        I_AM_SAVED                                                              = 11599,  -- ... I am saved.
        SILENCED_FOR_TOO_LONG_IN_THE_PRISON_OF                                  = 11600,  -- Silenced for too long in the prison of Dynamis, I can once again let my brazen call echo through this land!
        A_FEW_MORE_MOMENTS_IF_YOU_PLEASE                                        = 11601,  -- A few more moments, if you please...
        HELLO_THERE_I_AM_TEROUNALIVET_A_MILITARY_MUSICIAN                       = 11602,  -- Hello there. I am Terounalivet, a military musician of the Hydra Corps.
        YOU_VE_NEVER_HEARD_OF_ME_BEFORE_JOINING                                 = 11603,  -- You've never heard of me? Before joining the army I was quite the famous bard, mobbed by fans in every town I passed through.
        TO_BE_COMPLETELY_TRUTHFUL_I_AM_HEARTBROKEN_TO                           = 11604,  -- To be completely truthful, I am heartbroken to be giving up the %, the most famous of instruments, even to a fellow bard.
        BUT_AN_INSTRUMENT_ONLY_SHOWS_ITS_TRUE_WORTH                             = 11605,  -- But an instrument only shows its true worth when being played. This horn should be delighted to be passed on to such a talent as yourself.
        SHE_HAS_A_CAPRICIOUS_SOUL_BUT_DO_TREAT                                  = 11606,  -- She has a capricious soul, but do treat her well. And do not forget that even without a raging battle, you can still play a tune for the simple enjoyment of those around you...
        ID_11607                                                                = 11607,  -- ...
        HE_WAS_A_WONDERFUL_PERFORMER                                            = 11608,  -- He was a wonderful performer.
        LET_US_BE_ON_OUR_WAY_OUR_TOUR                                           = 11609,  -- Let us be on our way. Our tour of the world has only just begun...
        THE_IRNC_HAS_DISPATCHED_ME_TO_HELP_SUPPORT                              = 11610,  -- The IRNC has dispatched me to help support all those who wish to participate in Conflict.
        BEFORE_YOU_CAN_TAKE_PART_IN_THIS_CONFLICT                               = 11611,  -- Before you can take part in this Conflict event, you must first possess %. You can obtain one from your nation's Conflict Commander, [Excenmille, stationed in Northern San d'Oria./Invincible Shield, stationed in the Metalworks in Bastok./Mhabi Molkot, stationed in Heavens Tower in Windurst.]
        ONLY_ADVENTURERS_WHO_HAVE_ACHIEVED_RANK_3_OR                            = 11612,  -- Only adventurers who have achieved rank 3 or higher may take part in official Ballista matches. Please return when you have proven your loyalty to your home nation.
        HOWEVER_IF_YOU_STILL_WISH_TO_TAKE_PART                                  = 11613,  -- However, if you still wish to take part in Ballista, participation in matches held within Diorama Abdhaljs-Ghelsba is open to all citizens of Vana'diel.
        WHAT_SERVICES_DO_YOU_REQUIRE                                            = 11614,  -- What services do you require?
        WHAT_CAN_I_HELP_YOU_WITH_NOTHING_THE                                    = 11615,  -- What can I help you with? Nothing. The upcoming Ballista matches. The Ballista schedule. A teleport to the Ballista match. The rules of Ballista. Borrow/Return %. Borrow/Return %. Borrow/Return %. The upcoming Brenner matches. A teleport to the Brenner match (Lv #). The rules of Brenner. Borrow/Return %. Borrow/Return %.
        I_AM_ALLOWED_TO_TELEPORT_BALLISTA_PARTICIPANTS_TO                       = 11616,  -- I am allowed to teleport Ballista participants to the site of the next match in exchange for % or # Ballista [Point/Points]. This service is available from twenty-four hours before the start of the match, up until the end of the match.
        CAN_BE_RECEIVED_AFTER_PARTICIPATING_IN_BALLISTA_OR                      = 11617,  -- % can be received after participating in Ballista, or in the event one is not able to participate due to an influx (or lack) of entries.
