        I_M_A_TRAVELING_MOOGLE_ALWAYS_ON_THE                                    = 12133,  -- I'm a traveling Moogle, always on the road... In search of the secrets of true strength, kupo.
        AND_THIS_TIME_I_THINK_I_MIGHT_HAVE                                      = 12134,  -- And this time I think I might have found one. That's why I'm visiting Maat to see what he thinks, kupo.
        I_COULD_FILL_YOU_IN_ON_THE_DETAILS                                      = 12135,  -- I could fill you in on the details, but you don't look like you'd understand what I have to say. Come back when you think you've got some more seasoning under your belt, kupo...
        I_VE_DISCOVERED_A_WAY_TO_INCREASE_THE                                   = 12136,  -- I've discovered a way to increase the potential of those who have reached their limits. However, I haven't found anyone to pass that method on to, kupo. Hey, you look pretty tough. How would you like to be my guinea...errr, assistant?
        WAIT_A_MINUTE_I_REMEMBER_YOU_I_ALREADY                                  = 12137,  -- Wait a minute! I remember you! I already filled you in on the secrets of the Moogle Merit Management system, kupo! Stop wasting your time here; get fighting, kupo!
        BECOME_HIS_ASSISTANT_LET_S_DO_IT_NO                                     = 12138,  -- Become his assistant? Let's do it! No way! Tell me more...
        EXCELLENT_KUPO_AHEM_I_SHALL_NOW_PASS_ON                                 = 12139,  -- Excellent, kupo... Ahem! I shall now pass on to you the secrets of the Moogle Merit Management system. Use this legendary method to extend your limits. Watch as your strength soars beyond the stars, kupo!
        NOW_WHEN_THE_LEVEL_OF_YOUR_MAIN_JOB                                     = 12140,  -- Now, when the level of your main job has reached 75 or higher, a new button, Merit Points, will appear under Status in the main menu.
        PRESS_THIS_BUTTON_TO_CHANGE_EXPERIENCE_ACCUMULATION_MODES               = 12141,  -- Press this button to change experience accumulation modes as well as adjust skills and attributes. Just remember, you can only adjust your attributes while in your Mog House or Mog Garden, kupo!
        CASTS_A_STRANGE_SPELL_ON_YOU                                            = 12142,  -- casts a strange spell on you...
        HMMM_THAT_DIDN_T_WORK_KUPO_I_GUESS                                      = 12143,  -- Hmmm... That didn't work, kupo... I guess I still have some research to do. We'll have to put the experiment on hold for a while.
        HUH_WHAT_GOOD_IS_AN_ADVENTURER_THAT_S                                   = 12144,  -- Huh? What good is an adventurer that's not willing to take on a little adventure? Well, come back to me if you ever change your mind, kupo...
        BEEN_WORKING_HARD_OR_HARDLY_WORKING_KUPO_REMEMBER                       = 12145,  -- Been working hard, or hardly working, kupo? Remember that by pressing the Merit Points button in the Status menu, you can check merit point totals, change experience accumulation modes, and adjust skills and attributes.
        OHO_KUPO_OR_PERHAPS_YOU_RE_LOOKING_TO                                   = 12146,  -- Oho, kupo! Or perhaps you're looking to transcend your limits? Because that could also be arranged...
        ASK_ABOUT_MERIT_POINTS_YES_NO                                           = 12147,  -- Ask about merit points? Yes. No.
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_ASK_ABOUT_EXCEEDING_YOUR_LIMITS                           = 12148,  -- What will you ask about? Exceeding your limits. Merit points. Nothing.
        WELL_IF_YOU_EVER_NEED_A_REFRESHER_YOU                                   = 12149,  -- Well, if you ever need a refresher, you know where I'll be, kupo!
        OR_PERHAPS_YOU_VE_FINALLY_MUSTERED_THE_COURAGE                          = 12150,  -- Or perhaps you've finally mustered the courage to conquer your inner limits, kupo?
        BEFORE_YOU_RUSH_INTO_ANYTHING_LET_ME_INFORM                             = 12151,  -- Before you rush into anything, let me inform you of the disclaim...errr, the details of the method, kupo. Have you ever stopped to wonder what happens to all the experience you accumulate after maxing out your level?
        IN_RECENT_MONTHS_I_HAVE_DISCOVERED_THAT_THIS                            = 12152,  -- In recent months, I have discovered that this type of experience builds up in your body in a completely different form--a type of super experience, if you will. I have given this phenomenon the name limit points, kupo!
        WHEN_YOU_ACCUMULATE_TEN_THOUSAND_OF_THESE_POINTS                        = 12153,  -- When you accumulate ten thousand of these points, they are magically transformed into an even more super type of experience--super-duper experience, if you will. I call these ultra-special points merit points, kupo!
        BUT_THAT_IS_NOT_ALL_I_HAVE_DISCOVERED                                   = 12154,  -- But that is not all I have discovered. I think I have also come across a method to manage those points and use them to boost the levels of your body and mind beyond their current limits! I call it Moogle Merit Management, kupo!
        I_CAN_TELL_BY_THE_LOOK_ON_YOUR                                          = 12155,  -- I can tell by the look on your face that you're pretty interested, kupo. So, what would you like to know?
        ASK_ABOUT_HOW_TO_ACCUMULATE_MERIT_POINTS_HOW                            = 12156,  -- Ask about... How to accumulate merit points. How to adjust attributes. Nothing at this time.
        WELL_YOU_ALREADY_KNOW_THAT_BY_REACHING_LEVEL                            = 12157,  -- Well, you already know that by reaching level 75 you're ready to start collecting limit points, right, kupo?
        WELL_BEFORE_YOU_BEGIN_DON_T_FORGET_THAT                                 = 12158,  -- Well, before you begin, don't forget that you have to press the Merit Points button in the Status menu.
        IT_ONLY_APPEARS_WHEN_YOUR_MAIN_JOB_IS                                   = 12159,  -- It only appears when your main job is level 75 or higher, kupo.
        BY_PRESSING_THIS_BUTTON_YOU_CAN_TOGGLE_BETWEEN                          = 12160,  -- By pressing this button, you can toggle between experience point accumulation mode and limit point accumulation mode, kupo.
        IN_EXPERIENCE_POINT_ACCUMULATION_MODE_YOU_WILL_GAIN                     = 12161,  -- In experience point accumulation mode, you will gain normal EXP after every battle until you reach the maximum...
        WHILE_IN_LIMIT_POINT_ACCUMULATION_MODE_YOU_WILL                         = 12162,  -- ...while in limit point accumulation mode, you will receive limit points after every battle. It's that easy, kupo!
        OH_AND_BY_THE_WAY_IF_YOU_ARE                                            = 12163,  -- Oh, and by the way--if you are still in experience point accumulation mode after you've reached your maximum amount of EXP, any battles fought from that moment on will earn you limit points, regardless of the mode you are in, kupo!
        NORMALLY_YOU_CAN_ONLY_ACCUMULATE_LIMIT_POINTS_WHEN                      = 12164,  -- Normally, you can only accumulate limit points when you're playing a job that has reached level 75 or higher. However, there is one exception, kupo!
        WHEN_A_JOB_CAPABLE_OF_RECEIVING_LIMIT_POINTS                            = 12165,  -- When a job capable of receiving limit points has been reduced via a level restriction, you can still earn limit points by defeating enemies!
        JUST_DON_T_FORGET_TO_SWITCH_MODES_BEFORE                                = 12166,  -- Just don't forget to switch modes before heading out on a hunting trip! When you're in limit point accumulation mode, the color of the text in the Status window will change a little to let you know, kupo!
        FINALLY_IF_YOU_LEVEL_DOWN_OR_SWITCH_JOBS                                = 12167,  -- Finally, if you level down or switch jobs while in limit point accumulation mode, you will automatically be switched back to experience point accumulation mode.
        AH_AND_ONE_MORE_POINT_OF_ADVICE_YOU                                     = 12168,  -- Ah, and one more point of advice: You can always check the amount of limit points and merit points you have earned by viewing the Merit Point menu.
        UMMM_FIRST_OF_ALL_YOU_CAN_CHECK_THE                                     = 12169,  -- Ummm, first of all, you can check the number of merit points you have accumulated by pressing the Merit Points button under Status in the main menu.
        THE_DATA_I_HAVE_COLLECTED_SO_FAR_TELLS                                  = 12170,  -- The data I have collected so far tells me that it is quite difficult to raise these attributes, and that there seems to be a limit to the amount any certain attribute can be boosted, kupo.
        IT_ALSO_SEEMS_THAT_CERTAIN_ATTRIBUTES_AND_SKILLS                        = 12171,  -- It also seems that certain attributes and skills are connected in some way. I call these groups categories.
        FOR_EXAMPLE_IMAGINE_THE_ATTRIBUTES_IN_THE_HP                            = 12172,  -- For example, imagine the attributes in the HP/MP category can be raised a combination of seven times, kupo.
        THAT_MEANS_IF_YOU_RAISE_YOUR_MAX_HP                                     = 12173,  -- That means if you raise your Max HP five times, you can only raise your Max MP two times.
        IN_OTHER_WORDS_YOU_CANNOT_RAISE_ALL_OF                                  = 12174,  -- In other words, you cannot raise all of the attributes to their limits. The body must maintain a certain balance, or it will explode! Or something like that, kupo.
        THERE_IS_ALSO_A_WAY_TO_LOWER_ATTRIBUTES                                 = 12175,  -- There is also a way to lower attributes that have been pushed past their limits. Unfortunately, every time this is tried, the merit points used to originally raise that attribute are lost, kupo...
        OH_AND_FINALLY_THERE_ARE_SOME_ATTRIBUTES_AND                            = 12176,  -- Oh, and finally, there are some attributes and skills in the same category that have different limits. I'm still not sure about all of these, so I'd suggest asking some of your level 75 buddies for advice, kupo!
        HRM_HMMM_I_NEED_A_LITTLE_TIME_ALONE                                     = 12177,  -- Hrm? Hmmm... I need a little time alone to think... Would you mind coming back a little later, kupo?
        ID_0_4_1_5_6_7                                                          = 12178,  -- 0:# 4:# 1:# 5:#:# 6:#:# 7:#
        I_HAD_A_FEELING_THAT_S_WHAT_YOU                                         = 12179,  -- I had a feeling that's what you'd say, kupo! Well, Maat? How about it?
        WE_STAND_ON_THE_CUSP_OF_A_NEW                                           = 12180,  -- We stand on the cusp of a new era. It's the Goddess-given duty of an old warrior like me to prepare the younger generation to follow in my footsteps. And who better than a young man/woman] who's met every challenge sent his/her] way?
        YOU_CAN_SAY_THAT_AGAIN_MY_FRIEND                                        = 12181,  -- You can say that again, my friend!
        NO_DOUBT_YOU_VE_HEARD_OF_THE_MOG                                        = 12182,  -- No doubt you've heard of the mog tablets--those stone slabs engraved with the timeless wisdom of King Kupofried the Great that have been popping up periodically throughout the land.
        THE_TABLETS_HOLD_MANY_SECRETS_THAT_WE_MOOGLES                           = 12183,  -- The tablets hold many secrets that we moogles have yet to unravel, kupo. Why are our wings purple? Why are our noses red? How can we better assist our adventuring friends?
        WHY_I_WAS_JUST_HAVING_A_DISCUSSION_WITH                                 = 12184,  -- Why, I was just having a discussion with a friend of mine from the Magian Mooglehood on the very subject... That's when it hit me on the head like a herd of hecteyes!
        WHAT_IF_THE_ANCIENT_MOOGLE_ARTS_COULD_BE                                = 12185,  -- What if the ancient moogle arts could be used to augment not only adventurers' possessions, but the adventurers themselves, kupo!?
        USING_MY_KNOWLEDGE_OF_MERIT_POINTS_AND_DRAWING                          = 12186,  -- Using my knowledge of merit points--and drawing upon the martial mastery of Maat here--I've whipped up a method that just might work! What say you, adventurer? Care to be my test subject?
        COURSE_NOBODY_D_BLAME_YOU_FOR_NOT_TRUSTIN                               = 12187,  -- 'Course, nobody'd blame you for not trustin' the little devil. I'm not even sure I do. Heh heh heh...
        IS_AN_ADVENTURER_WHO_WOULD_SPURN_GREATER_STRENGTH                       = 12188,  -- Is an adventurer who would spurn greater strength truly an adventurer? Come, now! What have you got to lose, kupo?
        GIVE_IT_A_GO_KUPO_WILL_I_EVER                                           = 12189,  -- Give it a go, kupo? Will I ever! Not today.
        MARVELOUS_MAGNIFICENT_FIRST_I_LL_NEED_YOU_TO                            = 12190,  -- Marvelous! Magnificent! First, I'll need you to bring me # .
        THEY_RE_NEEDED_TO_CHANNEL_THE_ANCIENT_MOOGLE                            = 12191,  -- They're needed to channel the ancient moogle magic, you see. You'll also have to accumulate # merit point[/s] to provide the necessary energy to trigger the reaction, kupo.
        I_LL_BE_SITTIN_THIS_ONE_OUT_I                                           = 12192,  -- I'll be sittin' this one out, I fear. I may have mastered the martial arts, but I know better than to get mixed up with moogle mumbo-jumbo. Heh heh heh... Now go get 'em!
        SAY_IT_AIN_T_SO_KUPO_AH_BUT                                             = 12193,  -- Say it ain't so, kupo! Ah, but it is not a moogle's place to question the judgment of an accomplished adventurer such as yourself. Come back if you ever have a change of heart.
        HAVE_YOU_ACQUIRED_THE_AND_MERIT_POINT_NEEDED                            = 12194,  -- Have you acquired the # and # merit point[/s] needed to transcend your limits, kupo?
        IF_SO_THEN_TRADE_ME_THE_AND_WE                                          = 12195,  -- If so, then trade me the # and we'll be on our way! My wings are aflutter with anticipation!
        OR_DID_YOU_JUST_DROP_BY_TO_HEAR                                         = 12196,  -- Or did you just drop by to hear about merit points, kupo?
        THE_ANCIENT_MOOGLE_INCANTATION_REQUIRES_AND_MERIT_POINT                 = 12197,  -- The ancient moogle incantation requires # and # merit point[/s], kupo.
        SPECTACULAR_STUPENDOUS_LET_S_GET_STARTED_SHALL_WE                       = 12198,  -- Spectacular! Stupendous! Let's get started, shall we? If you'll just excuse me for a moment, kupo...
        YOO_HOOOOOO_MISTER_MAGIAN_MOOGLE_MAN_YES_YOU                            = 12199,  -- Yoo-hoooooo! Mister Magian Moogle man! Yes, you! Over here!
        WHAT_IS_IT_THIS_TIME_AND_YOU_D                                          = 12200,  -- What is it this time? And you'd do well to adopt a more courteous tone when addressing your elders, kupo...
        I_D_CALL_YOU_BY_YOUR_PROPER_NAME                                        = 12201,  -- I'd call you by your proper name if you'd actually tell anyone what it is! But nooo, the Magian Mooglehood must ever be shrouded in secrecy, kupo...
        YOU_WOULD_MAKE_MOCK_OF_THE_WISDOM_OF                                    = 12202,  -- You would make mock of the wisdom of your forefathers, kupo!?
        I_VE_A_MIND_TO_KU_POUND_THE                                             = 12203,  -- (I've a mind to ku-pound the both of them into the next millennium if they don't settle down...)
        ANYHOW_IF_YOU_WOULD_JUST_CROUCH_DOWN_RIGHT                              = 12204,  -- Anyhow, if you would just crouch down right here, kupo...
        MUMBLE_GRUMBLE_I_AM_READY_KUPO                                          = 12205,  -- <Mumble, grumble>... I am ready, kupo.
        EXCELLENT_OUR_MAGIAN_FRIEND_HERE_WILL_FIRE_A                            = 12206,  -- Excellent! Our magian friend here will fire a potent dose of moogle magic directly at you. All you have to do, my dear adventurer, is stay alive! Easy breezy, wouldn't you say, kupo?
        NOW_KUPO                                                                = 12207,  -- Now, kupo!
        THIS_IS_RECKLESS_EVEN_FOR_THESE_MOOGLES_SENDS                           = 12208,  -- (This is reckless even for these moogles. Sends a shiver up my spine, it does...)
        FEELS_A_SUDDEN_SURGE_OF_POWER_WELL_UP                                   = 12209,  -- % feels a sudden surge of power well up from the pit of his/her] stomach, coursing through his/her] veins and limbs...!
        KUPO_HO_IT_WOULD_SEEM_THE_PROCEDURE_HAS                                 = 12210,  -- Kupo-ho! It would seem the procedure has gone off precisely as we predicted!
        THAT_IT_HAS_KUPO_I_MUST_SAY_THE                                         = 12211,  -- That it has, kupo. I must say, the sheer stamina of these adventurers never ceases to astound me.
        MY_FRIEND_YOU_VE_BEEN_THE_PERFECT_TEST                                  = 12212,  -- My friend, you've been the perfect test subject...<ahem>...I mean, you are clearly an ideal heir for the powers of the moogle ancients. Should our research bear further fruit, you shall be among the first to know!
        BUT_WHY_ARE_YOU_STILL_STANDING_AROUND_HERE                              = 12213,  -- But why are you still standing around here? There's a whole new world waiting for you to explore, kupo!
        YOUR_LEVEL_LIMIT_IS_NOW_80                                              = 12214,  -- Your level limit is now 80!
        LET_ME_GUESS_KUPO_YOU_HAVE_CAUGHT_WORD                                  = 12215,  -- Let me guess, kupo. You have caught word of my latest miraculous method for padding the already-puissant powers of adventurers like yourself.
        YES_THE_POSITIVELY_ESURIENT_EXPRESSION_ON_YOUR_FACE                     = 12216,  -- Yes, the positively esurient expression on your face tells me all I need know.
        IS_THERE_NO_POINT_AT_WHICH_YOUR_PENCHANT                                = 12217,  -- Is there no point at which your penchant for power will be sated, kupo?
        IT_CANNOT_BE_EASY_WALKING_AROUND_AS_A                                   = 12218,  -- It cannot be easy, walking around as a veritable avatar of avarice and avidity.
        STILL_I_VE_TAKEN_A_LIKING_TO_YOUR                                       = 12219,  -- Still, I've taken a liking to your kind, kupo. And since you were such a wonderful guinea pig last time, I'd be positively elated to experiment upon you again!
        THAT_SAID_I_MUST_WARN_YOU_THAT_I                                        = 12220,  -- That said, I must warn you that I'm still working out some of the kinks. I can give you no guarantees this time.
        THAT_IS_TO_SAY_DON_T_COME_CRYING                                        = 12221,  -- That is to say, don't come crying to me if your level of strength ends up plunging precipitously, kupo!
        ARE_YOU_STILL_KEEN_FOR_THE_CHALLENGE                                    = 12222,  -- Are you still keen for the challenge?
        GIVE_IT_A_GO_KUPO_WILL_I_EVER_2                                         = 12223,  -- Give it a go, kupo? Will I ever! On second thought...
        EVER_THE_CONFIDENT_ONE_I_SEE_VERY_WELL                                  = 12224,  -- Ever the confident one, I see. Very well! Go procure the # needed for the procedure...
        AND_STORE_YOUR_SPIRITUAL_ENERGIES_TO_THE_TUNE                           = 12225,  -- ...And store your spiritual energies to the tune of # merit [point/points], and we'll give it a go, kupo!
        YOU_SURE_YOU_WANT_TO_GO_AHEAD_WITH                                      = 12226,  -- You sure you want to go ahead with this, %? This moogle mumbo-jumbo gets sketchier and sketchier each time, if you ask me.
        IS_THAT_SO_VERY_WELL_I_CANNOT_FAULT                                     = 12227,  -- Is that so? Very well. I cannot fault you for exercising a modicum of moderation, kupo.
        HAVE_YOU_ACQUIRED_THE_AND_MERIT_POINT_NEEDED_2                          = 12228,  -- Have you acquired the # and # merit point[/s] needed to transcend your limits?
        THEN_TRADE_THEM_TO_ME_AND_WE_SHALL                                      = 12229,  -- Then trade them to me and we shall begin the festivities, kupo!
        OR_DID_YOU_JUST_DROP_BY_TO_ASK                                          = 12230,  -- Or did you just drop by to ask me about merit points? Because I would be happy to oblige, kupo.
        MY_LATEST_MARVEL_OF_MOOGLE_MAGIC_REQUIRES_AND                           = 12231,  -- My latest marvel of moogle magic requires # and # merit point[/s], kupo.
        SPLENDID_SUPERLATIVE_IN_THAT_CASE_WITHOUT_FURTHER_ADO                   = 12232,  -- Splendid! Superlative! In that case, without further ado...
        YOO_HOOOOOO_MISTER_MAGIAN_MOOGLE_MAN_OVER_HERE                          = 12233,  -- Yoo-hoooooo! Mister Magian Moogle man! Over here, kupo!
        YES_YES_I_M_COMING_ALREADY_AND_KEEP                                     = 12234,  -- Yes, yes... I'm coming already. And keep your voice down, will you? I could hear your hooting and hollering from a malm away, kupo...
        SEEMS_THE_POOR_FELLA_S_RESIGNED_HIMSELF_TO                              = 12235,  -- (Seems the poor fella's resigned himself to his fate...)
        SAME_DEAL_AS_LAST_TIME_GOT_IT_KUPO                                      = 12236,  -- Same deal as last time. Got it, kupo? And today, we'll also be recruiting the services of a very special guest!
