        PLEASE_PRISHE_DO_YOU_HEAR_WHAT_YOU_ARE                                  = 12712,  -- Please, Prishe! Do you hear what you are saying!?
        HOW_CAN_I_LET_YOU_OFFER_YOUR_VERY                                       = 12713,  -- How can I let you offer your very existence to Promathia? There must be another way...!
        CALM_YOURSELF_ULMIA_PRISHE_WILL_NOT_BE_COMING                           = 12714,  -- Calm yourself, Ulmia. Prishe will not be coming with us.
        THE_LAST_VERSE_OF_THE_MEMORIA_DE_LA                                     = 12715,  -- The last verse of the Memoria de la S^tona no longer exists, and there is no weapon left to battle the Twilight God.
        PITTING_THE_FULL_FORCE_OF_JEUNO_AGAINST_THE                             = 12716,  -- Pitting the full force of Jeuno against the wyrms is our only recourse.
        THERE_IS_NO_OTHER_WAY_TO_SAVE_THE                                       = 12717,  -- There is no other way to save the children of Altana from extinction.
        BUT_MISS_MILDAURION_WHAT_ABOUT_ME                                       = 12718,  -- But Miss Mildaurion! What about me?
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL_THE_JEUNOAN_ARMADA_IS_PREPARED                          = 12719,  -- Lady Esha'ntarl! The Jeunoan Armada is prepared for battle!
        I_MUST_GO_BEYOND_THE_SEA_OF_ENDLESS                                     = 12720,  -- I must go. Beyond the sea of endless clouds.
        CARDINAL_MILDAURION                                                     = 12721,  -- Cardinal Mildaurion!
        PRISHE_ULMIA_IT_IS_ONLY_A_MATTER_OF                                     = 12722,  -- Prishe. Ulmia. It is only a matter of time until Jeuno becomes a war zone.
        I_WILL_PREPARE_AN_AIRSHIP_FOR_YOUR_RETURN                               = 12723,  -- I will prepare an airship for your return to Tavnazia.
        PROTECT_THAT_WHICH_IS_MOST_DEAR_TO_YOU                                  = 12724,  -- Protect that which is most dear to you.
        DAMMIT_THERE_S_NO_WAY_IN_HELL_IT                                        = 12725,  -- Dammit! There's no way in hell it's ending this way! It's time to put it all on the line!
        PRISHE_3                                                                = 12726,  -- Prishe!?
        ULMIA                                                                   = 12727,  -- %! Ulmia!
        I_KNOW_YOU_GUYS_CAN_DO_IT                                               = 12728,  -- I know you guys can do it!
        YOU_RE_STRONG_ENOUGH_NOW_TO_BEAT_THE                                    = 12729,  -- You're strong enough now to beat the hell out of me when I become Promathia...
        LISTEN_THERE_IS_SOMEONE_IN_SELBINA_WHO_KNOWS                            = 12730,  -- Listen, there is someone in Selbina who knows the fifth verse. Her memory is a little shoddy, though...
        FIND_THE_FIFTH_VERSE                                                    = 12731,  -- Find the fifth verse!
        I_NEED_YOU_TO_DO_THIS_YOU_HEAR                                          = 12732,  -- I need you to do this! You hear me!?
        I_CANNOT_PRISHE_WAIT                                                    = 12733,  -- I cannot...! Prishe, wait!
        ULMIA_I_HAVE_HEARD_THE_ENTIRE_STORY                                     = 12734,  -- Ulmia, I have heard the entire story.
        LOUVERANCE                                                              = 12735,  -- Louverance!?
        THIS_MUST_BE_THE_GUIDANCE_OF_ALTANA_THE                                 = 12736,  -- This must be the guidance of Altana. The girl with a shoddy memory in Selbina is well known to me.
        AND_I_ALSO_HAPPEN_TO_POSSESS_THE_MEANS                                  = 12737,  -- And I also happen to possess the means to revive her past. Let us be on our way.
        WHAT_IS_THERE_A_GIRL_IN_SELBINA_WITH                                    = 12738,  -- What? Is there a girl in Selbina with a serious case of amnesia?
        HOW_WOULD_I_KNOW_I_M_ALWAYS_CONFINED                                    = 12739,  -- How would I know? I'm always confined to my post here in Jeuno. You're the adventurer. Why don't you know these things?
        THOSE_THREE_TARUTARU_BROUGHT_TO_JEUNO_BY_NAG                            = 12740,  -- Those three Tarutaru brought to Jeuno by Nag'molada have been granted amnesty by Lady Esha'ntarl.
        HOWEVER_I_DON_T_BELIEVE_THEY_HAVE_MUCH                                  = 12741,  -- However, I don't believe they have much of a future here in the Duchy.
        ONCE_YOU_HAVE_ANGERED_IT_WOULD_TAKE_NO                                  = 12742,  -- Once you have angered [the Armathrwn Society/the archduke], it would take no less than a miracle to regain [their/his] trust.
        IT_APPEARS_YOU_CAUGHT_UP_WITH_THE_ARMADA                                = 12743,  -- %! It appears you caught up with the armada.
        I_HEARD_THE_REPORT_THE_ATTACK_AGAINST_BAHAMUT                           = 12744,  -- I heard the report. The attack against Bahamut failed, but we have dealt him a critical blow.
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL_IS_TO_JOIN_THE_MAIN                                     = 12745,  -- Lady Esha'ntarl is to join the main fleet and lead our forces in a mass assault.
        SHE_MENTIONED_THAT_SHE_WOULD_LIKE_TO_MEET                               = 12746,  -- She mentioned that she would like to meet with you all before the attack commences. You are to meet her for a confidential briefing in the tavern in Upper Jeuno.
        DO_NOT_KEEP_LADY_ESHA_NTARL_WAITING_MAY                                 = 12747,  -- Do not keep Lady Esha'ntarl waiting. May victory in battle be yours.
        CAPTAIN_WOLFGANG_HAS_ASKED_ME_TO_REMIND_YOU                             = 12748,  -- Captain Wolfgang has asked me to remind you that you are to hurry to the Marble Bridge in Upper Jeuno.
        IT_SOUNDED_AS_IF_IT_WAS_URGENT_YOU                                      = 12749,  -- It sounded as if it was urgent. You had best be on your way!
        RECENTLY_THERE_HAVE_BEEN_NO_SIGNS_OF_NAG                                = 12750,  -- Recently, there have been no signs of Nag'molada or those annoying Tarutaru entering the Grand Duke Palace.
        I_HEARD_FROM_ONE_OF_THE_GUARDS_THAT                                     = 12751,  -- I heard from one of the guards that the Tarutaru were seen riding an airship to Bastok, but as for Nag'molada...
        THE_PALACE_IS_OFTEN_THE_SITE_FOR_GRAND                                  = 12752,  -- The palace is often the site for grand banquets that are attended by dignitaries from every nation. In times like these, we do our utmost to see that the needs of our important visitors are met.
        RECENTLY_HAS_BEEN_REQUESTING_THE_ODDEST_THINGS_FROM                     = 12753,  -- Recently, [Lord Nag'molada/Lady Esha'ntarl] has been requesting the oddest things from the palace staff.
        THESE_REQUESTS_APPEAR_TO_BE_FOR_OBJECTS_DESIRED                         = 12754,  -- These requests appear to be for objects desired by guests of the Duchy.
        THESE_REQUESTS_APPEAR_TO_BE_FOR_OBJECTS_DESIRED_2                       = 12755,  -- These requests appear to be for objects desired by guests of our eminent official.
        IF_THE_REQUESTED_ITEMS_COULD_BE_FOUND_IN                                = 12756,  -- If the requested items could be found in Jeuno, nay, in the markets of any country, we would endeavor to procure them.
        HOWEVER_MANY_OF_THESE_OBJECTS_ARE_NOT_AVAILABLE                         = 12757,  -- However, many of these objects are not available for purchase. I am in quite a quandary, as you can see.
        PERHAPS_IF_I_WERE_TO_OFFER_A_REWARD                                     = 12758,  -- Perhaps if I were to offer a reward, you would be so kind as to locate these items on my behalf?
        WOULD_YOU_BE_SO_KIND_CERTAINLY_I_AM                                     = 12759,  -- Would you be so kind? Certainly. I am afraid not.
        THE_FOLLOWING_ITEMS_HAVE_BEEN_REQUESTED_AND_MY                          = 12760,  -- The following items have been requested: %, %, and %. My future employment rests in your hands.
        THE_FOLLOWING_ITEMS_HAVE_BEEN_REQUESTED_AND_MY_2                        = 12761,  -- The following items have been requested: %, %, %, and %. My future employment rests in your hands.
        THE_FOLLOWING_ITEMS_HAVE_BEEN_REQUESTED_AND_MY_3                        = 12762,  -- The following items have been requested: %, %, %, %, and %. My future employment rests in your hands.
        LORD_NAG_MOLADA_OFTEN_RECEIVES_GUESTS_OF_ALL                            = 12763,  -- Lord Nag'molada often receives guests of all kinds, but I have never before been besieged with such bizarre requests.
        THIS_IS_THE_FIRST_TIME_LADY_ESHA_NTARL                                  = 12764,  -- This is the first time Lady Esha'ntarl has ever made such a request of the palace staff. Furthermore, I do believe this is the first time she has personally received guests...
        WHILE_I_AM_CURIOUS_TO_KNOW_WHAT_KIND                                    = 12765,  -- While I am curious to know what kind of guests we are entertaining, a good servant does not intrude on the business of his employer.
        AH_SPLENDID_IT_APPEARS_YOU_HAVE_BEEN_SUCCESSFUL                         = 12766,  -- Ah, splendid. It appears you have been successful. You have my most heartfelt gratitude.
        WHY_WOULD_THE_GUESTS_OF_BE_SO_ENCHANTED                                 = 12767,  -- Why would the guests of [Lord Nag'molada/Lady Esha'ntarl] be so enchanted with these barbaric objects?
        OH_DEAR_BUT_I_MUST_WATCH_MY_MANNERS                                     = 12768,  -- Oh dear, but I must watch my manners. Please forgive my indiscretion. Here is your reward.
        THESE_ITEMS_WERE_AVAILABLE_AT_THE_AIR_TRAVEL                            = 12769,  -- These items were available at the air travel agency? Well, one learns something new every day. Your reward, as promised.
        TO_SEE_AN_ARRAY_OF_SUCH_OBJECTS_REKINDLES                               = 12770,  -- To see an array of such objects rekindles my desire to visit the Far East. How aromas of the unknown inspire our imagination! Here is your reward.
        I_AM_SURE_ANY_CHILD_S_EYES_WOULD                                        = 12771,  -- I am sure any child's eyes would light up at a collection of toys such as this.
        I_MUST_ADMIT_TO_BEING_QUITE_INTERESTED_IN                               = 12772,  -- I must admit to being quite interested in these myself. One never forgets the joy of one's youth. Your reward, sir/madame].
        PERHAPS_THIS_IS_A_GIFT_FOR_THE_LADY                                     = 12773,  -- Perhaps this is a gift for the lady of the house? These items are not of the highest quality...
        BUT_I_MUST_NOT_PRESUME_TO_JUDGE_THE                                     = 12774,  -- But I must not presume to judge the guests of [Lord Nag'molada/Lady Esha'ntarl]. Please accept your reward.
        YOUR_ASSISTANCE_IS_GREATLY_APPRECIATED_I_AM_CERTAIN                     = 12775,  -- Your assistance is greatly appreciated. I am certain [Lord Nag'molada/Lady Esha'ntarl]'s guests will be most satisfied with your efforts.
        EMPTINESS_POSSIBLE_WEAKNESSES_HMMM                                      = 12776,  -- ...Emptiness...... ......Possible weaknesses... Hmmm......
        GREETINGS_ADVENTURER_I_AM_HARITH_ALCHEMIST_AND_MEMBER                   = 12777,  -- Greetings, adventurer. I am Harith, alchemist and member of a certain prestigious society here in Jeuno.
        PERCHANCE_YOU_HAVE_HEARD_OF_CREATURES_KNOWN_AS                          = 12778,  -- Perchance you have heard of creatures known as the Empty? Currently, other alchemists in the society are working feverishly on methods to manipulate these mysterious beasts.
        WOULD_YOU_LIKE_ME_TO_CONTINUE                                           = 12779,  -- Would you like me to continue?
        WELL_PLEASE_GO_ON_I_M_BUSY_AT                                           = 12780,  -- Well...? Please, go on. I'm busy at the moment.
        I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_TAKING_UP_YOUR_VALUABLE_TIME                            = 12781,  -- I apologize for taking up your valuable time. May fortune smile upon you in your journey.
        THE_EMPTY_ARE_A_COLD_AND_HOLLOW_SPECIES                                 = 12782,  -- The Empty are a cold and hollow species--their very existence a void of nothingness. They possess no feeling, no will, no purpose... It is this lack of characteristics that makes them powerful, as they have no known weaknesses.
        HOWEVER_DEEP_WITHIN_THEIR_DARK_SHELLS_WE_HAVE                           = 12783,  -- However, deep within their dark shells we have discovered that something does exist--that something being a fragment of a memory lost in the pages of time.
        IF_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_HAVE_THE_FORTUNE_OF                                    = 12784,  -- If you happen to have the fortune of coming across one of these incomplete memories on your journeys, bring it to me and I shall purify it into a form known as anima using the methods discovered by the society.
        BY_STUDYING_THE_VARIOUS_TYPES_OF_MEMORIES_LEFT                          = 12785,  -- By studying the various types of memories left by the Empty, we may be able to discover their strengths and weaknesses.
        IF_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_HAVE_THE_FORTUNE_OF_2                                  = 12786,  -- If you happen to have the fortune of coming across one of these incomplete memories on your journeys, bring it to me and I shall purify it into a form known as anima using the methods discovered by the society.
        IN_ADDITION_TO_THESE_MEMORY_FRAGMENTS_WE_ARE                            = 12787,  -- In addition to these memory fragments, we are also collecting %, %, and % to help us better understand how these creatures evolved. Worry not, as you will be duly rewarded for any and all contributions.
        YES_THIS_IS_DEFINITELY_THE_MEMORY_OF_ONE                                = 12788,  -- Yes... This is definitely the memory of one of the Empty--and in quite excellent condition, I must say.
        I_CAN_SYNTHESIZE_IT_INTO_A_CONCENTRATED_FORM                            = 12789,  -- I can synthesize it into a concentrated form of anima; however, I will require a small fee of # gil.
        YOU_HAND_HARITH_THE_AND_GIL                                             = 12790,  -- You hand Harith the % and # gil.
        WHAT_A_REMARKABLE_SPECIMEN_THIS_MAY_BE_THE                              = 12791,  -- What a remarkable specimen! This % may be the key to unlocking the secrets of the Empty!
        HERE_PLEASE_ACCEPT_THIS_AS_A_TOKEN_OF                                   = 12792,  -- Here, please accept this as a token of my gratitude.
        I_WILL_BEGIN_THE_SYNTHESIS_RIGHT_AWAY_PLEASE                            = 12793,  -- I will begin the synthesis right away. Please wait a few moments.
        AH_WHAT_A_HEAVENLY_GLOW                                                 = 12794,  -- Ah, what a heavenly glow!
        BY_THROWING_THIS_ANIMA_BACK_AT_THE_EMPTY                                = 12795,  -- By throwing this anima back at the Empty, they will temporarily regain a splinter of consciousness. It is during this time that you may be able to find their weaknesses.
