        WE_VE_BEEN_WAITING_FOR_YOUR_ARRIVAL_MR                                  = 12922,  -- We've been waiting for your arrival Mr./Ms.]... Ah, yes, here it is--Mr./Ms.] %. Congratulations on your team's victory in the Ballista Royale preliminaries. You have successfully earned your ticket to the finals!
        COME_TO_THINK_OF_IT_I_KNEW_THAT                                         = 12923,  -- Come to think of it, I knew that Mr./Ms.]...%...yes, Mr./Ms.] %'s team would win all along! There was just something different about you... Something that smelled...like a winner, of course!
        AHEM_ANYWAY_NOW_LET_ME_PRESENT_YOU_WITH                                 = 12924,  -- Ahem! Anyway, now let me present you with your prize and a new title. I'm looking forward to seeing your name in my register again in the near future! Au Revoir!
        AH_WE_VE_BEEN_WAITING_FOR_YOU_ARRIVAL                                   = 12925,  -- Ah, we've been waiting for you arrival Mr./Ms.] %. (You see? Win enough times and I'm bound to remember your name!) Congratulations on your team's victory in the Ballista Royale Grand Tournament!
        I_KNEW_THAT_YOU_WERE_TALENTED_BUT_IT                                    = 12926,  -- I knew that you were talented, but it looks like you also had a smite of fortune on your side. How much did you pay off Lady Luck to have her smile down on only you? Hah hah hah... I'm sorry. That wasn't very funny...
        BUT_SERIOUSLY_THE_BLOOD_YOU_SPILLED_THE_TEARS                           = 12927,  -- But seriously, the blood you spilled, the tears you shed, the sweat you...you...sweat--all of these made you and your companions that much stronger. It was truly your hard work and perserverance that lead you to victory. Though, I knew all along that your team would win.
        AHEM_NOW_LET_ME_PRESENT_YOU_WITH_YOUR                                   = 12928,  -- Ahem! Now let me present you with your royale prize and new title, fit for a champion! Good show, Lord/Lady] %!
