        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_APPOINTMENT                 = 12935,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Appointment to Jeuno(pt.1). Appointment to Jeuno(pt.2). Jeuno(pt.1). Jeuno(pt.2). A New Journey(pt.1). A New Journey(pt.2). Magicite/San d'Orian Embassy. Magicite/Bastokan Embassy. Magicite/Windurstian Embassy. Magicite/Grand Duke Palace(pt.1). Magicite/Davoi. Magicite/Beadeaux. Magicite/Castle Oztroja. Magicite/Grand Duke Palace(pt.2).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_SHATTERING                  = 12936,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Shattering Stars(pt.1). Shattering Stars(pt.2). Shattering Stars(pt.3). Beat Around the Bushin. Ducal Dupe(pt.1). Ducal Dupe(pt.2). Beyond the Sun. Chameleon Capers. Storms of Fate(pt.1). Storms of Fate(pt.2). Shadows of the Departed(pt.1). Shadows of the Departed(pt.2). Apocalypse Nigh. Expanding Horizons. Beyond the Stars(pt.1). Beyond the Stars(pt.2). A Trial in Tandem(pt.1). A Trial in Tandem(pt.2). A Trial in Tandem, Redux. Dormant Powers Dislodged(pt.1). Dormant Powers Dislodged(pt.2). Dormant Powers Dislodged(pt.3). Prelude to Puissance. Beyond Infinity(pt.1). Beyond Infinity(pt.2). Martial Mastery(pt.1). Martial Mastery(pt.2).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_DYNAMIS                     = 12937,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Dynamis - The Shrouded Land(pt.1). Dynamis - The Shrouded Land(pt.2). Dynamis Interloper. Bravura. Fellow Points. Waking the Colossus(pt.1). Waking the Colossus(pt.2). Battle on a New Front(pt.1). Battle on a New Front(pt.2). VW Op. #126: Qufim Incursion(pt.1). VW Op. #126: Qufim Incursion(pt.2). A Cait Calls(pt.1). A Cait Calls(pt.2). A New Menace(pt.1). A New Menace(pt.2). No Rest for the Weary(pt.1). No Rest for the Weary(pt.2). Glimmer of Hope. Trust (Cherukiki). Trust (Maat).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_BELOW                       = 12938,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Below the Arks. A Vessel Without a Captain. Branded. For Whom the Verse Is Sung(pt.1). For Whom the Verse Is Sung(pt.2). A Place to Return. More Questions Than Answers(pt.1). More Questions Than Answers(pt.2). Flames in the Darkness. The Chains Fall Free.
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_EASTERLY                    = 12939,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Easterly Winds. Unraveling Reason. Light of Judgment(pt.1). Light of Judgment(pt.2).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_CALL                        = 12940,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Call to Serve(pt.1). Call to Serve(pt.2). Call to Serve(pt.3). Call to Serve(pt.4). Call to Serve(pt.5). Call to Serve(pt.6). Call to Serve(pt.7). Call to Serve(pt.8). Call to Serve(pt.9). Maat on the Rampage(pt.1). Maat on the Rampage(pt.2).
        OUT_OF_MY_WAIT_JUST_A_MOMENT_LET                                        = 12941,  -- Out of my... Wait just a moment. Let me have a good look at you...
        YES_YOU_MAY_BE_OF_SOME_USE_TO                                           = 12942,  -- Yes... You may be of some use to me after all.
        MY_NAME_IS_VENESSA_I_HAVE_TRAVELED_FROM                                 = 12943,  -- My name is Venessa. I have traveled from my homeland far to the west to hone my skills under the supervision of the ducal alchemists.
        I_AM_CURRENTLY_STUDYING_THE_PHENOMENON_KNOWN_AS                         = 12944,  -- I am currently studying the phenomenon known as the Emptiness and how its byproducts can be better utilized in my field.
        MY_RECENT_RESEARCH_HAS_SHOWN_THAT_IN_ADDITION                           = 12945,  -- My recent research has shown that in addition to the variety of creatures that roam the plains of Promyvion, there are a handful of even stronger manifests that dwell deep within towers that loom above the vast expanses of darkness.
        TO_CONTINUE_MY_WORK_I_REQUIRE_FRESH_REMNANTS                            = 12946,  -- To continue my work, I require fresh remnants of these rare beasts. Of course, your efforts will not go unrewarded.
        WILL_YOU_ACCEPT_MY_OFFER_OF_COURSE_NOT                                  = 12947,  -- Will you accept my offer? Of course. Not today. Tell me more. You've lost me.
        THEN_YOU_ARE_WASTING_MY_TIME                                            = 12948,  -- Then you are wasting my time.
        I_HAVE_TOLD_YOU_ENOUGH                                                  = 12949,  -- I have told you enough!
        THEN_YOU_ARE_OF_NO_USE_TO_ME                                            = 12950,  -- Then you are of no use to me. Begone!
        EXCELLENT                                                               = 12951,  -- Excellent.
        ACCORDING_TO_DATA_COLLECTED_BY_THE_DUCHY_THERE                          = 12952,  -- According to data collected by the Duchy, there are several different locations around Vana'diel where the Empty thrive. Adventurers have given these realms the name Promyvion.
        IF_MY_HYPOTHESIS_IS_CORRECT_I_BELIEVE_THERE                             = 12953,  -- If my hypothesis is correct, I believe there are four types of special remnants--one to coincide with each area. Which area do you wish to investigate?
        TRAVEL_TO_NOWHERE_AT_THIS_TIME_THE_SPIRE                                = 12954,  -- Travel to... Nowhere at this time. The Spire of Holla. The Spire of Dem. The Spire of Mea. The Spire of Vahzl.
        IF_YOU_HAVE_NO_INTENTIONS_OF_ASSISTING_ME                               = 12955,  -- If you have no intentions of assisting me, then stop wasting my time!
        YOU_SAY_THEN_YOU_WILL_NEED_THIS                                         = 12956,  -- [Holla/Dem/Mea/Vahzl], you say? Then you will need this %.
        WAIT_JUST_A_MOMENT_I_REMEMBER_YOU                                       = 12957,  -- Wait just a moment... I remember you.
        WHILE_I_APPRECIATE_YOUR_ASSISTANCE_I_DO_NOT                             = 12958,  -- While I appreciate your assistance, I do not have any more censers to aid you on your travels into Promyvion. I must ask you to return at a later date.
        YES_I_MAY_BE_ABLE_TO_PROVIDE_YOU                                        = 12959,  -- Yes, I may be able to provide you with another % on ( Earth time) and not a day sooner.
        HERE_YOU_MAY_HAVE_THIS_ONE_BUT_TAKE                                     = 12960,  -- Here, you may have this one, but take care not to lose it. These artifacts are extremely difficult to come by, and I have only a limited supply.
        AND_IF_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_COME_ACROSS_ONE                                    = 12961,  -- And if you happen to come across one of the rare remnants that I seek, bring it directly to me. Only then will you receive your reward.
        WHAT_IS_THIS_YOU_SAY_YOU_FOUND_SOMETHING                                = 12962,  -- What is this? You say you found something that may be of interest?
        YES_YES_WITH_THIS_I_CAN_PROVE_MY                                        = 12963,  -- Yes... Yes! With this I can prove my ability to the society! I am guaranteed a position within their ranks for sure!
        HM_YOUR_REWARD_OH_I_DO_REMEMBER_PROMISING                               = 12964,  -- Hm? Your reward? Oh, I do remember promising you something if you succeeded at your mission. How about this %? I don't think the society will be missing it.
        OUT_OF_MY_WAIT_JUST_A_MOMENT_YOU                                        = 12965,  -- Out of my... Wait just a moment. You wouldn't happen to have returned because you wish to delve into the depths of Promyvion once more, would you?
        WELL_THAT_S_WHY_I_M_HERE_I                                              = 12966,  -- Well? That's why I'm here. I was just passing by.
        I_HAVE_NEITHER_THE_TIME_NOR_PATIENCE_TO                                 = 12967,  -- I have neither the time nor patience to be bothered by every ignorant cretin that happens to wander by. Begone!
        LADY_ESHA_NTARL_S_SHIP_HAS_RETURNED                                     = 12968,  -- %! Lady Esha'ntarl's ship has returned.
        THIS_IS_EXCELLENT_TIMING_I_WAS_ORDERED_TO                               = 12969,  -- This is excellent timing. I was ordered to find you and ask that you proceed to the Marble Bridge--the tavern in Upper Jeuno.
        MY_DUTY_HERE_IS_DONE_I_MUST_NOW                                         = 12970,  -- My duty here is done. I must now journey to each nation and report that the Wyrmking Bahamut no longer poses a threat.
        I_HEAR_THAT_THIS_DEVELOPMENT_IS_ALL_THANKS                              = 12971,  -- I hear that this development is all thanks to you and your companions. You have the gratitude of all Jeunoans.
        I_HAVE_AWAITED_YOUR_RETURN_YOU_MUST_TELL                                = 12972,  -- I have awaited your return, %. You must tell me all that has happened.
        AFTER_CLASHING_WITH_OUR_ARMY_SEVERAL_TIMES_THE                          = 12973,  -- After clashing with our army several times, the dragons suddenly broke off their attack and disappeared into the distant clouds.
        THERE_WERE_VOICES_RAISED_IN_SUPPORT_OF_HUNTING                          = 12974,  -- There were voices raised in support of hunting the wyrms into extinction, but for the moment we have returned to resupply and reconsider our position.
        NOW_THAT_YOU_ARE_HERE_I_CAN_FINALLY                                     = 12975,  -- Now that you are here, I can finally be certain.
        AM_I_TO_ASSUME_FROM_YOUR_JUBILANT_FEATURES                              = 12976,  -- Am I to assume from your jubilant features that the Keeper of the Apocalypse has been defeated?
        HAS_THE_KEEPER_BEEN_DEFEATED_COMPLETELY_WHO_CAN                         = 12977,  -- Has the keeper been defeated? Completely. Who can say?
        I_KNEW_IT_BAHAMUT_SENSED_THE_KEEPER_S                                   = 12978,  -- I knew it! Bahamut sensed the keeper's downfall and pulled his forces out of battle...
        TELL_ME_WHAT_MOMENTOUS_EVENTS_TRANSPIRED_IN_THE                         = 12979,  -- Tell me. What momentous events transpired in the Celestial Capital?
        ON_CAPE_RIVERNE_THE_IMAGES_THAT_FLOWED_INTO                             = 12980,  -- On Cape Riverne, the images that flowed into me from Selh'teus...
        THEY_WERE_OF_THE_INCOMPLETE_PARADISE_AL_TAIEU                           = 12981,  -- They were of the incomplete Paradise, Al'Taieu...
        THE_PEOPLE_OF_AL_TAIEU_RETURNED_TO_THEIR                                = 12982,  -- The people of Al'Taieu returned to their deity ten thousand years ago. Returned to Promathia...
        OPENING_THE_GATES_OF_PARADISE_IS_A_METAPHOR                             = 12983,  -- Opening the Gates of Paradise is a metaphor for restoring the shattered mothercrystal. A way to return the world to its original state.
        THE_WORLD_BECOMES_A_PARADISE_AND_ITS_PEOPLE                             = 12984,  -- The world becomes a paradise, and its people ascend to godhood. The Dawnmaiden Yve'noile has memories of witnessing the true form of the great goddess Altana.
        YVE_NOILE_SPOKE_TO_ME_BEFORE_WE_PARTED                                  = 12985,  -- Yve'noile spoke to me before we parted ways.
        SHE_SAID_AS_I_GAZED_UPON_HER_PERFECTION                                 = 12986,  -- She said, As I gazed upon her perfection, I realized I could not be a part of her. I wondered who I could possibly be.
        THAT_WAS_WHEN_SHE_BEGAN_HER_RESEARCH_INTO                               = 12987,  -- That was when she began her research into the race of people.
        AFTER_SHIFTING_HER_FOCUS_TO_THE_INEXPLICABLE_APPEARANCE                 = 12988,  -- After shifting her focus to the inexplicable appearance of the Kuluu phenomenon, Yve'noile became aware of the darkness that resided within us all.
        HER_REALIZATION_LED_HER_TO_BETRAY_THE_KING                              = 12989,  -- Her realization led her to betray the king and his son, and adamantly oppose any plan to open the Gates of Paradise.
        SHE_HAD_DISCOVERED_OUR_ORIGINS_AS_THE_CHILDREN                          = 12990,  -- She had discovered our origins as the children of Promathia...
        BUT_ALL_HAS_NOT_BEEN_RESOLVED                                           = 12991,  -- But all has not been resolved.
        THE_EMPTINESS_STILL_SEETHES_WITHIN_THE_MOTHERCRYSTALS                   = 12992,  -- The Emptiness still seethes within the mothercrystals.
        AND_THE_SURVIVING_ZILART_YET_CLING_DESPERATELY_TO                       = 12993,  -- And the surviving Zilart yet cling desperately to their shadowy plan of returning to Paradise.
        I_GAVE_UP_MY_LIFE_IN_TAVNAZIA_ALMOST                                    = 12994,  -- I gave up my life in Tavnazia almost thirty years ago to infiltrate the organization of the newly awakened Zilart.
        BUT_I_HAVE_BEEN_UNABLE_TO_STEM_THEIR                                    = 12995,  -- But I have been unable to stem their vast power on my own.
        HOWEVER_WE_NOW_HAVE_A_COMMON_ENEMY_IN                                   = 12996,  -- However, we now have a common enemy in the Emptiness. For a time, the people of this age will require the aid of the ancients.
        THE_ANCIENTS_TOO_WILL_NEED_YOUR_CONTINUING_HELP                         = 12997,  -- The ancients, too, will need your continuing help.
        SURELY_THE_DAWN_MAIDEN_HAS_BEQUEATHED_SOMETHING_OF                      = 12998,  -- Surely the Dawn Maiden has bequeathed something of value to her younger kin.
        I_WILL_FIND_OUT_WHAT_THIS_MAY_BE                                        = 12999,  -- I will find out what this may be, and speak with Archduke Kam'lanaut. He will heed my words.
