        THE_MARKET_IS_SATURATED_WITH_BIOGRAPHIES_OF_DAUNTLESS                   = 14291,  -- The market is saturated with biographies of dauntless adventurers triumphing over the Shadow Lord, and even exaggerated accounts of encounters with the Twilight God himself. If I want to distinguish myself from the rest, I need to find a different angle, something fresh and unique...
