        TIME_IS_OF_THE_ESSENCE_SO_I_LL                                          = 15016,  -- Time is of the essence, so I'll get straight to the heart of the matter. We are engaged in an operation of the utmost importance, and I thought you'd be just the man/woman] for the task.
        AS_YOU_MAY_HAVE_ALREADY_NOTICED_THE_VOIDWALKER                          = 15017,  -- As you may have already noticed, the Voidwalker threat grows more menacing by the day. In particular, the fiends we have encountered here in the vicinity of the Duchy are possessed of powers that dwarf their already-formidable brethren.
        I_HEREBY_AUTHORIZE_YOU_FOR_PARTICIPATION_IN_VOIDWATCH                   = 15018,  -- I hereby authorize you for participation in Voidwatch operations in the Jeuno region. Serve us well, and you will be duly compensated for your efforts.
        YOU_ARE_NOT_THE_ONLY_I_HAVE_RECRUITED                                   = 15019,  -- You are not the only [adventurer/Allied soldier] I have recruited for this operation. Should you chance upon any others, you may join up with them if you so choose. The Duchy--no, the entire realm--is counting on you, %. Do not let us down.
        SO_YOU_HAVE_FINALLY_COME_I_AM_MAWL                                      = 15020,  -- So you have finally come. I am Mawl'gofaur, aide to the Archduke and overseer of the Voidwatch operation in His Excellency's absence.
        I_HEAR_YOU_HAVE_PROVEN_YOURSELF_CAPABLE_ON                              = 15021,  -- I hear you have proven yourself capable on the field. The Grand Duchy has need of your services.
        THE_VOIDWALKER_THREAT_GROWS_EVER_MORE_GRAVE_BY                          = 15022,  -- The Voidwalker threat grows ever more grave by the day. The fiends that have been sighted in the immediate vicinity of Jeuno, in particular, possess powers unlike anything we've seen before.
        WERE_THE_DUCHY_TO_FALL_TO_THIS_EXTRADIMENSIONAL                         = 15023,  -- Were the Duchy to fall to this extradimensional menace, it would spell disaster for the realm. This should be evident to even a grunt such as yourself.
        IN_THE_NAME_OF_HIS_EXCELLENCY_KAM_LANAUT                                = 15024,  -- In the name of His Excellency Kam'lanaut, Archduke of Jeuno, I hereby authorize you for participation in all Voidwatch operations conducted under the Duchy's jurisdiction.
        MIND_YOU_YOU_ARE_NOT_THE_ONLY_ONE                                       = 15025,  -- Mind you, you are not the only one to whom I have bestowed this clearance. Should you chance upon any of the others, you may band together against the fiends. Or do not. It matters little to me so long as you succeed in your efforts.
        WE_LACK_FOR_CAPABLE_SOLDIERS_SO_DO_TRY                                  = 15026,  -- We lack for capable soldiers, so do try to stay alive. Now be off with you. More pressing matters require my attention.
        THE_ASSIGNMENT_OF_INDIVIDUAL_OBJECTIVES_WILL_BE_HANDLED                 = 15027,  -- The assignment of individual objectives will be handled by our officers stationed throughout the greater Jeuno region. Report to one posthaste to receive your orders.
        DO_NOT_FORGET_TO_REPORT_BACK_TO_AN                                      = 15028,  -- Do not forget to report back to an officer upon completing an objective, lest your accomplishments go overlooked.
        THAT_IS_ALL_YOU_ARE_DISMISSED                                           = 15029,  -- ...That is all. You are dismissed.
        I_REMIND_YOU_AGAIN                                                      = 15030,  -- I remind you again...
        AH_YOU_VE_RETURNED_YOUR_EXPLOITS_IN_THE                                 = 15031,  -- Ah, you've returned! Your exploits in the Jeuno operation have been remarkable to observe. On behalf of the entire Grand Duchy, I commend you.
        VERY_WELL_THE_NEXT_STEP_IS_CLEAR_I                                      = 15032,  -- ...Very well. The next step is clear. I hereby authorize you to participate in our Qufim operation.
        AGAIN_I_MUST_WARN_YOU_THE_ENEMY_YOU                                     = 15033,  -- Again, I must warn you. The enemy you face in Qufim will be unlike anything you've faced thus far.
        THE_VOIDWALKER_MENACE_GROWS_MORE_DIRE_WITH_EACH                         = 15034,  -- The Voidwalker menace grows more dire with each passing hour. Where do these beasts come from, and what brings them to our world? Sometimes it seems as if the tireless efforts of our researchers yield more questions than answers.
        AND_YET_WE_CAN_DO_NOTHING_BUT_CONTINUE                                  = 15035,  -- And yet we can do nothing but continue the fight. I'm counting on you, %.
        ON_BEHALF_OF_THE_GRAND_DUCHY_I_COMMEND                                  = 15036,  -- On behalf of the Grand Duchy, I commend your efforts in the Jeuno Voidwatch operation. Yet the battle is far from won.
        I_HEREBY_ISSUE_YOU_YOUR_NEXT_ASSIGNMENT_YOU                             = 15037,  -- I hereby issue you your next assignment. You are to travel to the Qufim region and assist in our operation there.
        THE_VOIDWALKER_MENACE_IS_AT_ITS_MOST_FIERCE                             = 15038,  -- The Voidwalker menace is at its most fierce in Qufim. We have already lost our share of capable men.
        DO_YOUR_BEST_NOT_TO_JOIN_THEM_NOW                                       = 15039,  -- Do your best not to join them. Now be along on your way.
        I_VE_RECEIVED_WORD_OF_YOUR_ACCOMPLISHMENTS_IN                           = 15040,  -- %! I've received word of your accomplishments in Qufim. Truly, your service to the Voidwatch has exceeded even my initial expectations.
        I_VE_RECEIVED_WORD_OF_YOUR_ACCOMPLISHMENTS_TRULY                        = 15041,  -- %! I've received word of your accomplishments. Truly, your service to the Voidwatch has exceeded even my initial expectations.
        AND_YET_IT_IS_HARDLY_THE_TIME_TO                                        = 15042,  -- And yet it is hardly the time to rejoice. You have seen it with your own eyes--no sooner is one fiend slain than another of its brethren emerges to take its place.
        WE_MUST_FIND_A_WAY_TO_SEAL_THE                                          = 15043,  -- We must find a way to seal the planar rifts. Then, and only then, will we be able to quash this extradimensional menace once and for all.
        EVEN_AS_WE_SPEAK_AN_ELITE_TEAM_OF                                       = 15044,  -- Even as we speak, an elite team of my best researchers works tirelessly to that very end. Sadly, the true nature of the rifts remains very much an enigma...
        AND_SO_I_HAVE_NO_CHOICE_BUT_TO                                          = 15045,  -- And so I have no choice but to employ capable adventurers such as yourself to keep the fiends at bay. As inefficient as it may seem, it is the best course of action available to us under these conditions.
        WE_ARE_COUNTING_ON_YOUR_CONTINUED_EFFORTS_IN                            = 15046,  -- We are counting on your continued efforts, %. In the meantime, take this for your service. May it serve you well.
        ADMIRABLE_WORK_IN_QUFIM_SOLDIER_I_DID_NOT                               = 15047,  -- Admirable work in Qufim, soldier. I did not think you had it in you. His Excellency has expressed great satisfaction in your accomplishments as well.
        AND_YET_WE_CANNOT_AFFORD_TO_BECOME_COMPLACENT                           = 15048,  -- And yet we cannot afford to become complacent. For each fiend we dispatch, a more abominable monstrosity rises to take its place.
        WE_HAVE_RECOVERED_MUCH_USEFUL_DATA_FROM_YOUR                            = 15049,  -- We have recovered much useful data from your encounters with the Voidwalkers. Data that an elite team of our best researchers works tirelessly to analyze.
