        YOU_LAID_THE_FOUNDATION_WITH_YOUR_PHYSICAL_ENHANCEMENTS                 = 15099,  -- You laid the foundation with your physical enhancements experiments, my fluttery, furry friend. I simply-wimply applied the finishing touches.
        BUT_LET_S_GET_TO_THE_HEART_OF                                           = 15100,  -- But let's get to the heart of the mattaru, %. What I've bestowed upon you today is but a foundation for powers that may yet be mastered.
        LISTEN_AND_LISTEN_WELL_LOOK_WITHIN_AND_TAKE                             = 15101,  -- Listen, and listen well. Look within and take stock of your merits, and you'll see a new path open to you.
