        LET_UP_NOT_IN_YOUR_TRAINING_THE_PATH                                    = 15108,  -- Let up not in your training, %. The path to true martial mastery lies before you. Now, if you'll excuse me, I've got some rarab tails t'--er, I mean, my trainin' to get back to.
        YOU_LEARNED_THE_SECRET_TECHNIQUE_OF_THE_BUSHIN                          = 15109,  -- You learned the secret technique of the bushin!
        YOU_VE_COME_SPLENDID_WE_REGRET_HAVING_TO                                = 15110,  -- You've come. Splendid. We regret having to summon you again so soon after your last tour of duty, but the Duchy has need of your services again.
        OUR_RESEARCH_TEAM_HAS_CONFIRMED_THE_PRESENCE_OF                         = 15111,  -- Our research team has confirmed the presence of new rifts in the greater three nations area.
        UNDER_NORMAL_CIRCUMSTANCES_THE_DEFENSE_EFFORT_WOULD_FALL                = 15112,  -- Under normal circumstances, the defense effort would fall under the jurisdiction of the local governments. This time, however, I fear the circumstances are far from normal.
        I_WILL_BE_FRANK_WITH_YOU_THE_STRENGTH                                   = 15113,  -- I will be frank with you, %. The strength of the enemy is beyond anything we've faced thus far.
        HERE_IS_YOUR_BADGE_OF_AUTHORIZATION_TAKE_IT                             = 15114,  -- Here is your badge of authorization. Take it and report to the Voidwatch officers stationed afield for further orders.
        ONCE_AGAIN_WE_HAVE_RECRUITED_OTHER_PROMISING_ADVENTURERS                = 15115,  -- Once again, we have recruited other promising adventurers to our cause. You may find it in your best interests to join up with them before taking on the enemy. We're counting on you, %.
        I_TRUST_YOU_VE_RECOVERED_FROM_YOUR_LAST                                 = 15116,  -- I trust you've recovered from your last tour of duty. If not, so be it. Full strength or no, the Duchy requires your service.
        DUCAL_RESEARCHERS_HAVE_ALERTED_US_TO_THE_PRESENCE                       = 15117,  -- Ducal researchers have alerted us to the presence of newly formed planar rifts in the vicinity of the three kingdoms.
        UNDER_NORMAL_CIRCUMSTANCES_WE_WOULD_LET_THE_NATIONS                     = 15118,  -- Under normal circumstances we would let the nations fend for themselves. We fear that this time, however, their limited resources and manpower will do little to stem the tide of this formidable enemy.
        HENCE_WE_TURN_TO_YOU_TAKE_THIS_BADGE                                    = 15119,  -- Hence, we turn to you. Take this badge of authorization and present it to our officers afield for further orders.
        WE_HAVE_RECRUITED_OTHERS_FOR_THE_EFFORT_AS                              = 15120,  -- We have recruited others for the effort as well. Join forces with them if you wish, or fight alone. Just remember: the success of the operation is more important than the life of any single soldier, including yours.
        AS_WE_TRUST_YOU_ARE_ALREADY_AWARE                                       = 15121,  -- As we trust you are already aware...
        DIRECT_SUPERVISION_OF_THE_VOIDWATCH_OPERATION_WILL_BE                   = 15122,  -- Direct supervision of the Voidwatch operation will be conducted by our officers dispatched to the three nations. You are to follow their instructions to the letter.
        ONCE_AGAIN_YOU_PROVE_THAT_THE_DUCHY_S                                   = 15123,  -- %. Once again you prove that the Duchy's faith in you was not misplaced.
        YOU_ARE_AN_ASSET_TO_THE_VOIDWATCH_AND                                   = 15124,  -- You are an asset to the Voidwatch. And yet the data we have recovered from your efforts yields as many questions as answers.
        THE_VOIDWALKER_MENACE_HAS_BEEN_QUIETED_FOR_NOW                          = 15125,  -- The Voidwalker menace has been quieted for now. Yet we would be fools to believe that our foe will remain silent for long.
        UNTIL_WE_CAN_IDENTIFY_AND_ELIMINATE_THE_SOURCE                          = 15126,  -- Until we can identify and eliminate the source of the threat, we have no recourse but to call upon you again.
        IN_THE_MEANTIME_TAKE_THIS_AS_RECOMPENSE_FOR                             = 15127,  -- In the meantime, take this as recompense for your efforts. I trust you shall put it to good use.
        WHAT_IS_THE_MEANING_OF_THIS_INTERRUPTION                                = 15128,  -- What is the meaning of this interruption!?
        MY_PARDONS_YOUR_EXCELLENCY_WE_VE_RECEIVED_DIRE                          = 15129,  -- My pardons. Your Excellency, we've received dire news from the field. Two new rifts have been confirmed at previously unbreached locations...
        HMPH_TWO_YOU_SAY                                                        = 15130,  -- Hmph. Two, you say?
        AYE_ONE_BURIED_IN_THE_SANDS_OF_THE                                      = 15131,  -- Aye. One buried in the sands of the Valkurm Dunes, the other on Buburimu Peninsula.
        YOUR_EXCELLENCY                                                         = 15132,  -- Your Excellency...?
        THIS_ADVENTURER_IS_A_VETERAN_VOIDWATCHER_I_WOULD                        = 15133,  -- This adventurer is a veteran Voidwatcher. I would have him/her] hear your findings as well.
        AT_PRESENT_IT_RESPONDS_TO_NEITHER_NOR_WE                                = 15134,  -- At present, it responds to neither % nor %. We are unable to gauge the potential danger of any Voidwalkers that may lie beyond.
        INTRIGUING_SO_THE_PORTAL_BETWEEN_DIMENSIONS_IS_NOT                      = 15135,  -- Intriguing. So the portal between dimensions is not yet fully formed...
        IT_IS_ONLY_A_MATTER_OF_TIME_BEFORE                                      = 15136,  -- It is only a matter of time before the monsters spring forth. Let up your watch not for a second, and send word the moment you detect anything amiss.
        SIR_YES_SIR                                                             = 15137,  -- Sir! Yes, sir!
        IT_WOULD_SEEM_YOUR_NEXT_MISSION_WILL_BEGIN                              = 15138,  -- It would seem your next mission will begin sooner rather than later, soldier.
        WE_WILL_AUTHORIZE_YOU_FOR_PARTICIPATION_AT_SUCH                         = 15139,  -- We will authorize you for participation at such time as it is necessary. In the meantime, I suggest you rest up and prepare yourself for the challenges ahead.
        TOO_MUCH_REMAINS_UNKNOWN_ABOUT_THESE_RIFTS_I                            = 15140,  -- Too much remains unknown about these rifts. I grow impatient with our researchers and their incessant pleas for more time.
        I_CONCUR_THE_SITUATION_THREATENS_TO_SPIRAL_OUT                          = 15141,  -- I concur. The situation threatens to spiral out of control. We cannot afford to play the dispassionate observer for much longer.
        HAS_PROVED_A_MOST_USEFUL_RESOURCE_IN_THE                                = 15142,  -- % has proved a most useful...resource...in the pursuit of our goals.
        AND_YET_THERE_ARE_LIMITS_TO_WHAT_ONE                                    = 15143,  -- And yet there are limits to what one adventurer--or even an army of them--can do. It seems that we have no choice but to get involved more...directly.
        YES_YOUR_EXCELLENCY                                                     = 15144,  -- ...Yes, Your Excellency.
        IT_WOULD_SEEM_THE_VOIDWATCH_EFFORT_IN_THE                               = 15145,  -- It would seem the Voidwatch effort in the three nations was a success. Once again, you prove yourself not entirely useless.
        THE_ARCHDUKE_WILL_BE_PLEASED_AND_YET_THE                                = 15146,  -- The Archduke will be pleased. And yet the Voidwalker menace persists.
        THE_DATA_WE_HAVE_RECOVERED_FROM_YOUR_LATEST                             = 15147,  -- The data we have recovered from your latest mission is...not promising.
        MORE_DETAILS_I_THINK_YOU_FORGET_YOUR_STATION                            = 15148,  -- More details? I think you forget your station, soldier. You will get the information you are authorized to receive, and no more.
        LET_IT_SUFFICE_TO_SAY_THAT_WE_WILL                                      = 15149,  -- Let it suffice to say that we will have need of your services again. Stay alive, and do not stray too far.
        I_AM_SURE_YOU_UNDERSTAND_WHY_WE_HAVE                                    = 15150,  -- I am sure you understand why we have summoned you on such short notice. Yes, it does indeed concern the Voidwalkers.
        RECENTLY_HOWEVER_SOME_NEW_FACTS_HAVE_COME_TO                            = 15151,  -- Recently, however, some new facts have come to light. Reports confirm a new substance that can be culled from those planes-walking fiends.
        IT_IS_SAID_TO_POSSESS_TWO_SEPARATE_FORMS                                = 15152,  -- It is said to possess two separate forms: one is that of a crystal, the other of a more granular structure resembling cruor. Its alabaster hue, however, serves to distinguish it from that vermilion currency.
        WHILE_IT_MAY_EXHIBIT_CRYSTALLINE_PROPERTIES_IT_IS                       = 15153,  -- While it may exhibit crystalline properties, it is unlike any specimen of crystal we have heretofore examined. The oft-used phrase shrouded in mystery does not begin to describe how it baffles even our most accomplished researchers.
        WE_MAY_HAVE_NOTHING_MORE_TO_GUIDE_US                                    = 15154,  -- We may have nothing more to guide us than conjecture, but we cannot discard the possibility that this mineral is an integral piece in the calamitous puzzle that Vana'diel faces. Do not hesitate to collect as large a sample as possible of this mysterious mineral.
        SHOULD_YOU_REQUIRE_FURTHER_INTELLIGENCE_SEEK_OUT_A                      = 15155,  -- Should you require further intelligence, seek out a Voidwatch Officer. As they are the ones who operate in the field, they should be privy to the most current of information.
        FURTHERMORE                                                             = 15156,  -- Furthermore...
        WHETHER_AS_HARDENED_STONE_OR_DUST_DEPOSITS_THIS                         = 15157,  -- Whether as hardened stone or dust deposits, this substance is less than abundant.
        VOIDWATCH_OFFICERS_SHOULD_BE_WILLING_TO_PART_WITH                       = 15158,  -- Voidwatch Officers should be willing to part with some samples, however, should you fail to harvest any off of Voidwalker corpses.
        NO_MATTER_THE_METHOD_BY_WHICH_YOU_OBTAIN                                = 15159,  -- No matter the method by which you obtain it, this mineral should shine new light on this catastrophe and allow you to more efficiently aid our cause.
        TO_THE_EXTENT_OF_OUR_KNOWLEDGE_THERE_IS                                 = 15160,  -- To the extent of our knowledge, there is no new planar rift activity, but you of all people should understand the spontaneous nature of these interdimensional disturbances. None of us can let our guard down for even a moment.
        ARCHDUKE_KAM_LANAUT_EXPECTS_GREAT_THINGS_OF_YOU                         = 15161,  -- Archduke Kam'lanaut expects great things of you as well. It is quite regrettable that he could not honor us with his presence today, but he is a busy man with many entice--er, engagements.
        NOW_THAT_YOU_UNDERSTAND_HOW_YOU_CAN_BE                                  = 15162,  -- Now that you understand how you can be of service, it is time you got to your duties. Let us conclude this parley.
        HMM_SOMETHING_S_NOT_RIGHT_HERE                                          = 15163,  -- Hmm...something's not right here.
        I_WOULD_HAVE_EXPECTED_THEIR_REPORTS_TO_HAVE                             = 15164,  -- I would have expected their reports to have arrived by now...
        WHO_S_THIS_THEN_AN_ADVENTURER_I_GATHER                                  = 15165,  -- Who's this then? An adventurer, I gather?
        WELL_ARE_YOU_OF_COURSE_NO                                               = 15166,  -- Well? Are you? Of course! No...
        PLEASE_FORGIVE_MY_INTRUSION                                             = 15167,  -- Please forgive my intrusion.
        I_WISH_YOU_WELL_IN_ALL_YOUR_ENDEAVORS                                   = 15168,  -- I wish you well in all your endeavors.
        TO_FIND_AN_ADVENTURER_SUCH_AS_YOURSELF_SO                               = 15169,  -- To find an adventurer such as yourself so quickly! Fortune indeed shines upon me this day!
        BUT_WHERE_ARE_MY_MANNERS_I_HAVE_NOT                                     = 15170,  -- But where are my manners? I have not yet introduced myself. I am Anastase, an emissary sent from the Sacred City of Adoulin.
        BUT_OF_COURSE_YOU_NEED_NOT_SAY_ANYTHING                                 = 15171,  -- But of course, you need not say anything. I know why you have sought me out.
        YOU_ARE_HERE_TO_ASSIST_ME_IN_SURVEYING                                  = 15172,  -- You are here to assist me in surveying the geomagnetic founts, yes?
        LEND_YOUR_AID_I_SHALL_NOT_INTERESTED_HEAR                               = 15173,  -- Lend your aid? I shall. Not interested. Hear more.
        I_SEE_I_MUST_ADMIT_TO_FEELING_A                                         = 15174,  -- I see. I must admit to feeling a twinge of disappointment, but I understand.
        MY_STAY_HERE_WILL_BE_A_LONG_ONE                                         = 15175,  -- My stay here will be a long one, so if you have a change of heart, please come and see me again.
        HAVE_YOU_CHANGED_YOUR_MIND_WILL_YOU_HELP                                = 15176,  -- Have you changed your mind? Will you help me study the geomagnetic founts?
        I_COME_FROM_THE_SACRED_CITY_OF_ADOULIN                                  = 15177,  -- I come from the Sacred City of Adoulin, an island that lies far to the west, beyond the great Sea of Zafmlug.
        FURTHER_STILL_BEYOND_THE_ISLAND_IS_THE_CONTINENT                        = 15178,  -- Further still beyond the island is the continent of Ulbuka, where a pristine expanse of nature sits unsullied by mortal hands.
        TALES_OF_MEN_AND_WOMEN_FROM_THE_MIDDLE                                  = 15179,  -- Tales of men and women from the Middle Lands who cannot resist the clarion call of a good deed left undone have stretched across the sea and reached my ears. Hearing these tales prompted me to make the arduous journey here.
        FOR_YOU_SEE_I_DESIRE_YOUR_ASSISTANCE_IN                                 = 15180,  -- For you see, I desire your assistance in our quest to pioneer the undeveloped lands of Ulbuka.
        I_HAD_HOPED_TO_SECURE_TRANSPORT_IN_ADVANCE                              = 15181,  -- I had hoped to secure transport in advance for those interested in cooperating with this enterprise.
        BUT_EXECUTING_A_PLAN_IS_NEVER_A_SIMPLE                                  = 15182,  -- But executing a plan is never a simple affair. Air and sea vessels are indeed available, but unsustainable in the long term due to the staggering distance between the two continents.
        YET_ONE_POSSIBILITY_EXISTS_IN_OUR_BELOVED_CITY                          = 15183,  -- Yet one possibility exists. In our beloved city, devices called waypoints allow the user to instantaneously move from one location to another.
        HOWEVER_I_AM_NOT_CERTAIN_WHETHER_THE_LEY                                = 15184,  -- However, I am not certain whether the ley lines to which these waypoints are attuned traverse the oceans to the Middle Lands. My first task, therefore, is to find locations suitable for such travel.
        ARE_NEEDED_TO_USE_OUR_WAYPOINTS_BUT_THEIR                               = 15185,  -- % are needed to use our waypoints, but their efficacy is dependent on recording the energies of certain geomagnetic founts.
        AS_PART_OF_THIS_MISSION_I_HAVE_BROUGHT                                  = 15186,  -- As part of this mission, I have brought with me several such %. What I would ask of you is that you take one to these various founts and attune it to them.
        UNFORTUNATELY_THERE_IS_PRECIOUS_LITTLE_TIME_TO_COLLECT                  = 15187,  -- Unfortunately, there is precious little time to collect this information.
        AS_I_HAVE_PREVIOUSLY_MENTIONED_MY_FERVENT_HOPE                          = 15188,  -- As I have previously mentioned, my fervent hope is that you will undertake this mission. The very fate of my homeland hangs in the balance.
        WHAT_I_ASK_IS_THAT_YOU_USE_TO                                           = 15189,  -- What I ask is that you use % to...oh?
        YOU_MEAN_TO_TELL_ME_THAT_YOU_ALREADY                                    = 15190,  -- You mean to tell me that you already possess %? Then this will be all the easier!
        THIS_IS_FOR_THE_MIDDLE_LANDS                                            = 15191,  -- This % is % for the Middle Lands.
        WHAT_I_WOULD_ASK_OF_YOU_IS_THAT                                         = 15192,  -- What I would ask of you is that you attune the % to the aforementioned geomagnetic founts.
        IF_THIS_SURVEY_IS_SUCCESSFUL_THEN_IT_WILL                               = 15193,  -- If this survey is successful, then it will surely guarantee a prosperous trading partnership for our two homelands.
        I_ALSO_IMAGINE_THAT_THERE_ARE_MANY_WHO                                  = 15194,  -- I also imagine that there are many who would both honor and value your accomplishment.
        YOUR_HELP_IS_SINCERELY_APPRECIATED_LET_ME_PRESENT                       = 15195,  -- Your help is sincerely appreciated. Let me present you with this %.
        ATTUNING_IT_TO_A_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_WILL_IF                              = 15196,  -- Attuning it to a geomagnetic fount will, if my calculations are correct, permit you to use the waypoints.
        I_HAVE_ALREADY_RECORDED_THE_ENERGIES_OF_THE                             = 15197,  -- I have already recorded the energies of the Ru'Lude Gardens fount. Please, travel throughout the world and proceed with your activities, and return to me when you have attuned it to another fount.
        HAVING_NEVER_BEEN_TO_THIS_LAND_I_AM                                     = 15198,  -- Having never been to this land, I am not familiar with the exact locations, but our powers of divination have given us a certain cryptic insight.
        ANY_QUESTIONS_TELL_ME_YOUR_PROGNOSTICATIONS_TELL_ME                     = 15199,  -- Any questions? Tell me your prognostications. Tell me about these waypoints. Explain all this to me. None in particular.
        WHICH_PROGNOSTICATION_NONE_ACTUALLY_HOW_DO_I_RECORD                     = 15200,  -- Which prognostication? None, actually. How do I record these founts? <Port>.[ /: Complete] <Dwelling>.[ /: Complete] <Spring>.[ /: Complete] <Fort>.[ /: Complete]
        QUWI_ORIHBHE_A_MEMBER_OF_OUR_MISSION_HAS                                = 15201,  -- Quwi Orihbhe, a member of our mission, has seen... A geomagnetic fount located in [a port named after a young woman/a dwelling located in plains dotted by craggy outcroppings/a gushing oasis bursting forth from the surrounding dunes/a hard-to-find locale carved out of rock].
        I_REALIZE_THAT_THESE_TIPS_MAY_CONFOUND_MORE                             = 15202,  -- I realize that these tips may confound more than confirm, but the features of this land are largely unbeknownst to me.
        YET_NOW_THAT_I_THINK_OF_IT_QUWI                                         = 15203,  -- Yet now that I think of it, Quwi did leave further clues behind...
        PURE_WHITE_BEACHES_CLAY_DISEMBOWELMENT                                  = 15204,  -- Pure white beaches... Clay... Disembowelment...
        A_LONG_NECKED_BEAST_A_CHEF_IN_SEARCH                                    = 15205,  -- A long-necked beast... A chef in search of meat from that beast... The Old Lady...
        A_WINDMILL_A_LARGE_LAKE_AN_ISLAND_WHERE                                 = 15206,  -- A windmill... A large lake... An island where sand stretches to the sky...
        SAMURAI_AND_NINJAS_PIRATES_CONTRABAND                                   = 15207,  -- Samurai and ninjas... Pirates... Contraband...
        WELL_THIS_CERTAINLY_IS_QUITE_PERPLEXING_I_ONLY                          = 15208,  -- Well, this certainly is quite perplexing. I only apologize that I cannot help you further.
        IF_YOU_SOLVE_THESE_RIDDLES_AND_FIND_A                                   = 15209,  -- If you solve these riddles and find a geomagnetic fount, all you must do is hold up your % to the location.
        QUITE_A_SIMPLE_TASK_NO                                                  = 15210,  -- Quite a simple task, no?
        I_SHALL_BE_WAITING_HERE_TO_COLLECT_YOUR                                 = 15211,  -- I shall be waiting here to collect your % when you have completed this endeavor.
        MANY_YEARS_HAVE_I_SPENT_RESEARCHING_AND_ANALYZING                       = 15212,  -- Many years have I spent researching and analyzing these phenomena. Sensing any changes in the object I have given you is merely a trifle.
        TO_A_LAYMAN_S_EYES_THOUGH_ANY_DEVIATIONS                                = 15213,  -- To a layman's eyes, though, any deviations are impossible to detect.
        MY_HOPE_IS_THAT_SHOULD_THESE_PORTALS_BECOME                             = 15214,  -- My hope is that, should these portals become fully active, even the uninitiated will be able to make such determinations with ease.
        I_AM_SURE_YOU_HAVE_NOTICED_THIS_MYSTERIOUS                              = 15215,  -- I am sure you have noticed this mysterious device resting at my side. In Adoulin, we refer to items of its ilk as waypoints.
        THESE_PORTALS_ENABLE_INSTANTANEOUS_TRANSPORTATION_BETWEEN_TWO_LOCATIONS = 15216,  -- These portals enable instantaneous transportation between two locations simply by holding up % to them.
        I_AM_SURE_THAT_NOW_YOU_UNDERSTAND_THE                                   = 15217,  -- I am sure that now you understand the implications of my calling--if the geomagnetic founts are as strong as our research implies, then the waypoints should function here, as well.
        AS_WE_RECORD_INFORMATION_ABOUT_THE_FOUNTS_WE                            = 15218,  -- As we record information about the founts, we should be able to warp between more locations.
        HOWEVER_THERE_IS_ALWAYS_A_PRICE_TO_BE                                   = 15219,  -- However, there is always a price to be paid for convenience. Warping consumes a tiny bit of energy extracted from certain types of crystals.
        THIS_ENERGY_WHICH_IN_MY_FIELD_S_PARLANCE                                = 15220,  -- This energy, which in my field's parlance is referred to as kinetic units, is imbued in % when extracted from these crystals.
        KINETIC_UNITS_ARE_CONSUMED_EACH_TIME_YOU_WARP                           = 15221,  -- Kinetic units are consumed each time you warp, meaning that periodic imbuing is necessary for continued use of the waypoints.
        AH_YES_BEFORE_I_FORGET_OTHER_MEMBERS_OF                                 = 15222,  -- Ah yes, before I forget--other members of my expedition have already gone to survey these locations.
        SHOULD_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_CROSS_PATHS_WITH_THEM                              = 15223,  -- Should you happen to cross paths with them, make sure to emphasize that I am still waiting for their reports.
        MAY_ALTANA_KEEP_YOU_SAFE_IN_THIS_QUEST                                  = 15224,  -- May Altana keep you safe in this quest.
        HAIL_AND_GOOD_TIDINGS_MAY_I_PLEASE_TAKE                                 = 15225,  -- Hail, and good tidings. May I please take a look at your %?
        ID_15226                                                                = 15226,  -- ...!
        THIS_THIS_IS_AMAZING                                                    = 15227,  -- This...this is amazing!
        YOU_HAVE_TRAVELED_TO_THE_LOCATIONS_I_HAVE                               = 15228,  -- You have traveled to the # locations I have requested and recorded the data in the geomagnetic founts there!
        ADVENTURERS_ARE_TRULY_AS_RELIABLE_AS_I_WAS                              = 15229,  -- Adventurers are truly as reliable as I was led to believe. All in a day's work, I suppose.
        YOU_HAVE_MY_UNDYING_GRATITUDE_FOR_YOUR_EFFORTS                          = 15230,  -- You have my undying gratitude for your efforts. Allow me to present this to you as a mere token of my appreciation.
        AS_AN_ASIDE_DID_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_MEET                                      = 15231,  -- As an aside, did you happen to meet with any of the other members of my expedition?
        THOUGH_A_BIT_WET_BEHIND_THE_EARS_THEIR                                  = 15232,  -- Though a bit wet behind the ears, their skills and talents are unparalleled.
        AMONG_THEIR_RANKS_ARE_GEOMANCERS_AND_RUNE_FENCERS                       = 15233,  -- Among their ranks are geomancers and rune fencers--a rare sight in the Middle Lands, to be sure.
        IF_YOU_WERE_TO_VISIT_ADOULIN_YOU_MAY                                    = 15234,  -- If you were to visit Adoulin, you may be able to find out about their secrets for yourself.
        FORGIVE_MY_LOOSE_TONGUE_SOME_THINGS_SHOULD_BE                           = 15235,  -- Forgive my loose tongue. Some things should be found out for oneself.
        MY_EFFORTS_NOW_ARE_FOCUSED_ON_OBTAINING_INFORMATION                     = 15236,  -- My efforts now are focused on obtaining information about any more geomagnetic founts that may exist. I may have more information for you at a later date.
        MY_FRIEND_IT_IS_GOOD_TO_SEE_YOU                                         = 15237,  -- %, my friend! It is good to see you again. With what may I assist you today?
        ANY_QUESTIONS_LET_S_EXPAND_THESE_WARP_OPTIONS                           = 15238,  -- Any questions? Let's expand these warp options. Any new predictions? What about these waypoints? What am I supposed to do again? None in particular.
        UTTERLY_MAGNIFICENT_I_SUPPOSE_ADVENTURERS_ALWAYS_HAVE_TO                = 15239,  -- Utterly magnificent! I suppose adventurers always have to have a sixth sense about these sorts of things.
        I_HAVE_JUST_RECEIVED_WORD_THAT_MY_COLLEAGUE                             = 15240,  -- I have just received word that my colleague, Quwi Orihbhe, has predicted the existence of geomagnetic founts in new lands.
        WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_HEAR_MORE_INFORMATION_ABOUT                           = 15241,  -- Would you like to hear more information about these hotspots?
        WHICH_SPOT_ARE_YOU_INTERESTED_IN_NONE_HOW                               = 15242,  -- Which spot are you interested in? None. How do I record data? <Green Light>.[ /: Complete] <Clear Waters>.[ /: Complete] <Crowned Tower>.[ /: Complete] <Deep Cliffs>.[ /: Complete] <Windmill>.[ /: Complete] <Dust Cloud>.[ /: Complete] <Lakeside>.[ /: Complete] <Swamps>.[ /: Complete] <Backbone>.[ /: Complete] <Crags>.[ /: Complete] <Silver>.[ /: Complete]
        HMM_LET_S_SEE                                                           = 15243,  -- Hmm, let's see... [A green light at the end of a dark prison/A roaring dragon bound for clear waters/A tower crowned with the name of an orchid/The depths of cliffs that cleave plains in twain/The power to run through a windmill-dotted land/The foot of a precipice where dust clouds rage/Crimson shears sleeping by a forested lakeside/Ceaseless raindrops in swampy land/A mountain range where dragon bones form an arc/Gigantic crags where undying feathers rain down/A corridor hidden by a silver shield]...
        ID_15244                                                                = 15244,  -- ...
        WOULD_THAT_I_COULD_HELP_YOU_MORE_BUT                                    = 15245,  -- Would that I could help you more, but this is the extent of Quwi's divination.
        YET_I_TRUST_THAT_ONE_SUCH_AS_YOURSELF                                   = 15246,  -- Yet I trust that one such as yourself, an adventurer of the highest caliber, will decipher these faint musings...
        AND_ELUCIDATE_WHAT_LIES_BEYOND                                          = 15247,  -- ...and elucidate what lies beyond!
        I_SHALL_REMAIN_HERE_WITH_EARS_TRAINED_FOR                               = 15248,  -- I shall remain here with ears trained for word of your success.
        AH_YES_I_HAD_BEEN_HOPING_YOU_WOULD                                      = 15249,  -- Ah yes, %. I had been hoping you would grace me with your presence.
        I_HAVE_JUST_RECEIVED_A_REPORT_FROM_QUWI                                 = 15250,  -- I have just received a report from Quwi Orihbhe that...hm?
        WHAT_IS_THIS_AURA_I_SENSE_COMING_FROM                                   = 15251,  -- What is this aura I sense coming from your %? May I...?
        ID_15252                                                                = 15252,  -- ...?
        YOU_YOU_HAVE_ALREADY_RECORDED_THE_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNTS                    = 15253,  -- ...! You...you have already recorded the geomagnetic founts!?
        IMPOSSIBLE_DOES_THIS_MEAN_THAT_YOU_TOO_POSSESS                          = 15254,  -- Impossible! Does this mean that you, too, possess the power of prognostication?
        OR_PERHAPS_ARE_THE_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNTS_OF_THE                            = 15255,  -- Or, perhaps, are the geomagnetic founts of the Middle Land so rich in power that...? No, such a conclusion goes in the face of decades of research!
        AH_FORGIVE_MY_SUDDEN_OUTBURST_YOUR_ACTIONS_HAVE                         = 15256,  -- Ah! Forgive my sudden outburst. Your actions have stirred latent emotions within me.
        SETTING_THAT_ASIDE_THERE_IS_NO_DENYING_THAT                             = 15257,  -- Setting that aside--there is no denying that you have recorded the information I desired.
        YOU_HAVE_CONVINCED_ME_THAT_THE_ABILITY_TO                               = 15258,  -- You have convinced me that the ability to further your scope of operations is a blessing like none other.
        I_PRESUME_IT_BEST_TO_OFFER_YOU_THIS                                     = 15259,  -- I presume it best to offer you this in compensation for your troubles...even though in this case, you have completed my task without any intervention on my part.
        THE_VIM_AND_VIGOR_OF_YOU_ADVENTURERS_SURELY                             = 15260,  -- The vim and vigor of you adventurers surely knows no bounds!
        TO_IMAGINE_THAT_ONE_COULD_ACCOMPLISH_MY_CHARGE                          = 15261,  -- To imagine that one could accomplish my charge without shedding as much as a drop of sweat! And now, for your reward.
        STILL_I_HAVE_ONE_CONCERN_MY_COMPATRIOTS_HAVE                            = 15262,  -- Still, I have one concern. My compatriots have yet to return from their dispatch.
        THOUGH_YOU_HAVE_INDICATED_TO_ME_THAT_THEY                               = 15263,  -- Though you have indicated to me that they are in good health, I remain concerned...
        EACH_MUST_HAVE_THEIR_OWN_REASONS_FOR_NOT                                = 15264,  -- Each must have their own reasons for not returning. With every step, a new journey...
        THEIR_COMMITMENT_TO_OUR_RESEARCH_MUST_PRECLUDE_THEIR                    = 15265,  -- Their commitment to our research must preclude their return. If that is so, then I must remain diligent as well!
        I_SHALL_INFORM_YOU_WHEN_I_HAVE_NEW                                      = 15266,  -- I shall inform you when I have new predictions in place, and pray that you will aid me yet again when the time comes.
        ANY_QUESTIONS_MUST_HAVE_MORE_WARP_DESTINATIONS_ANY                      = 15267,  -- Any questions? Must have more warp destinations! Any new founts? What about these waypoints? What do I do again? Thanks, but no thanks.
        I_SENSE_THE_HANDS_OF_FATE_HAVE_BOUND                                    = 15268,  -- I sense the hands of fate have bound us together through our mutually insatiable curiosity.
        AND_YES_MY_INTREPID_FRIEND_QUWI_ORIHBHE_HAS                             = 15269,  -- And yes, my intrepid friend, Quwi Orihbhe has found yet more locations for us...well, you...to examine.
        WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_HEAR_MORE                                             = 15270,  -- Would you like to hear more?
        WHICH_PREDICTION_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_HEAR_NONE                            = 15271,  -- Which prediction would you like to hear? None. How do I record the areas? <Abandoned Village>.[ /: Complete] <Malediction>.[ /: Complete] <Faeries>.[ /: Complete] <City Ruins>.[ /: Complete] <Grotto>.[ /: Complete] <Shrine>.[ /: Complete] <Forest>.[ /: Complete] <Urban Locale>.[ /: Complete] <Belfry>.[ /: Complete] <Darkness>.[ /: Complete]
        HMM_WHAT_CAN_I_GIVE_YOU_TO_GO                                           = 15272,  -- Hmm... What can I give you to go on? [A church standing in an abandoned village/Beyond a hall wrapped in curses/An abode of faeries worshipping a living god/A city swallowed by the land/An eroded cave where space twists and turns/A temple where those who have lost darkness reside/Moss that glistens deep within a gigantic tree/A city constructed by nomadic beastmen/Another beautiful ring of a bell/The farthest reaches of the blackest depths].
        WOULD_THAT_I_COULD_TELL_YOU_MORE_BUT                                    = 15273,  -- Would that I could tell you more, but as previously, I can only relay what was told to me.
        JUST_AS_YOU_HAVE_OVERCOME_PAST_TRIALS_AND                               = 15274,  -- Just as you have overcome past trials and tribulations, so too shall you triumph this day.
        I_BELIEVE_IN_YOU                                                        = 15275,  -- I believe in you!
        MAY_YOUR_STEPS_BE_SWIFT_AND_YOUR_BLADES                                 = 15276,  -- May your steps be swift and your blades true.
        AS_YOU_MOST_LIKELY_HAVE_PRESUMED_QUWI_ORHIBHE                           = 15277,  -- As you most likely have presumed, Quwi Orhibhe has...oh?
        THE_FOUNTS_ARE_ALREADY_RECORDED                                         = 15278,  -- ...! The founts are...already recorded!?
        WHAT_WHAT_SORCERY_IS_THIS                                               = 15279,  -- What...what sorcery is this?
        DO_YOU_HAVE_FEELERS_THROUGHOUT_THE_FAR_REACHES                          = 15280,  -- Do you have feelers throughout the far reaches of the land? Or...are you a wizard?
        MY_FEEBLE_MIND_CANNOT_COMPREHEND_HOW_YOU_HAVE                           = 15281,  -- My feeble mind cannot comprehend how you have already found the geomagnetic founts that have only just now been divined. H-how...
        I_DO_NOT_KNOW_BY_WHAT_MEANS_YOU                                         = 15282,  -- I do not know by what means you have obtained such information, but I sense that it was some extra-dimensional force...where information is contained for all to see.
        I_AM_PLEASED_THAT_YOU_HAVE_RETURNED_SAFELY                              = 15283,  -- I am pleased that you have returned safely. May I see your %?
        YOUR_EFFORTS_HAVE_TAKEN_YOU_TO_LANDS_BOTH                               = 15284,  -- Your efforts have taken you to lands both far and wide. I congratulate you on having trekked so far throughout Vana'diel.
        THERE_ARE_NO_WORDS_TO_DESCRIBE_HOW_I                                    = 15285,  -- There are no words to describe how I feel for all you have done. Even my most compelling reward is an insufficient prize.
        HAVE_YOU_GOTTEN_USED_TO_USING_OUR_WARP                                  = 15286,  -- Have you gotten used to using our warp technology? Is it to your liking?
        THE_THEORETICAL_MAGICAL_CALCULATIONS_BEHIND_THESE_WAYPOINTS_ARE         = 15287,  -- The theoretical magical calculations behind these waypoints are based on, if my records are correct, studies done here in the Middle Lands.
        I_WAS_BUT_A_FLEDGLING_RESEARCHER_AT_THAT                                = 15288,  -- I was but a fledgling researcher at that time, so I am a tad hazy on the details of it all, but my journey from Adoulin has more meaning in light of that fact.
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_KNOW_WHAT_ABOUT                                  = 15289,  -- What would you like to know? What about these waypoints? I need more information. Can I give you a hand with...you know? Thank you, and good day.
        HMM_WHATEVER_DO_YOU_MEAN                                                = 15290,  -- Hmm? Whatever do you mean?
        I_SUPPOSE_I_SHOULDN_T_HIDE_BEHIND_BLANK                                 = 15291,  -- I suppose I shouldn't hide behind blank stares...
        FOR_YOU_SEE_WARPING_TO_INCREDIBLY_DANGEROUS_LOCALES                     = 15292,  -- For you see, warping to incredibly dangerous locales is, at times, truly frightening. Though I am aware you chose this option out of curiosity...
        KNOWING_WHAT_I_HAVE_JUST_TOLD_YOU_WOULD                                 = 15293,  -- Knowing what I have just told you, would you still like to accept this task?
        ACCEPT_HIS_TASK_IT_COULDN_T_HURT_MUCH                                   = 15294,  -- Accept his task? It couldn't hurt...much. On second thought... Tell me more.
        A_DEAD_ADVENTURER_IS_OF_NO_USE_TO                                       = 15295,  -- A dead adventurer is of no use to anyone. I cannot fault you for choosing the better part of valor.
        WHAT_I_AM_ABOUT_TO_TELL_YOU_HAS                                         = 15296,  -- What I am about to tell you has never before occurred in Adoulin, so I admit to being at a bit of a loss.
        PARTIES_REPRESENTING_ER_FORMER_PATRONS_OF_THESE_WAYPOINTS               = 15297,  -- Parties representing, er, former patrons of these waypoints have reported certain...anomalies. Specifically, they occasionally fall down from the heavens. Splat.
        MY_CONFIDANTES_HAVE_BEEN_WORKING_TIRELESSLY_TO_DETERMINE                = 15298,  -- My confidantes have been working tirelessly to determine the root cause, and our working theory is that over time, the recorded information becomes weak and unstable.
        I_WOULD_ASK_THAT_YOU_TAKE_THIS_AND                                      = 15299,  -- I would ask that you take this % and warp to the problematic locales.
        ONCE_THERE_YOU_CAN_CONFIRM_THE_INTEGRITY_OF                             = 15300,  -- Once there, you can confirm the integrity of the spot and correct the recorded information as necessary.
        THIS_ALL_SOUNDS_MORE_COMPLICATED_THAN_IT_REALLY                         = 15301,  -- This all sounds more complicated than it really is. All you must do is re-attune the stone to the geomagnetic fount.
        AS_YOU_HAVE_LIKELY_GATHERED_THE_INSTABILITY_MEANS                       = 15302,  -- As you have likely gathered, the instability means that I cannot guarantee that you will arrive at your intended destination.
        YOU_COULD_END_UP_FACING_MONSTERS_TOOTH_AND                              = 15303,  -- You could end up facing monsters tooth and claw, or be surrounded by an impenetrable mist that seeps into your very soul.
        QUITE_FRAUGHT_WITH_PERIL_INDEED                                         = 15304,  -- Quite fraught with peril, indeed.
        YET_IF_ANYONE_COULD_ACCOMPLISH_THIS_TASK_IT                             = 15305,  -- Yet if anyone could accomplish this task, it would be you.
        Y_YOU_MEAN_IT_I_HAD_JUST_BEEN                                           = 15306,  -- Y-you mean it? I had just been bluffing, but you're really going to...?
        ARE_YOU_ABSOLUTELY_SURE_ADVENTURE_AWAITS_YOU_COULDN                     = 15307,  -- Are you absolutely sure? Adventure awaits! You couldn't pay me enough.
        AN_ADVENTURER_YOU_ARE_IN_THE_LITERAL_SENSE                              = 15308,  -- An adventurer you are, in the literal sense of the word!
        LET_ME_RESPOND_TO_YOUR_COURAGEOUS_REQUEST_WITH                          = 15309,  -- Let me respond to your courageous request with the utmost confidence!
        I_HEREBY_PRESENT_YOU_WITH_THIS_TAKE_IT                                  = 15310,  -- I hereby present you with this %. Take it with you to areas for which the recorded data has begun to deteriorate.
        THERE_ARE_SEVERAL_LOCATIONS_IN_QUESTION_WHICH_WILL                      = 15311,  -- There are several locations in question. Which will you choose?
        JUST_HOW_TOUGH_DO_YOU_WANT_THIS_TO                                      = 15312,  -- Just how tough do you want this to be? On second thought... Tough as butter. Tough as nails. Tough as diamond. I require further explanation.
        SO_BE_IT_THEN_I_HAVE_PREPARED_THE                                       = 15313,  -- So be it then. I have prepared the waypoint for your use.
        MAY_YOU_COME_BACK_IN_ONE_PIECE                                          = 15314,  -- May you come back in one piece!
        BACK_FOR_MORE_VERY_WELL_PICK_YOUR_POISON                                = 15315,  -- Back for more? Very well. Pick your poison.
        THAT_TWINKLE_IN_YOUR_EYE_IS_THAT_SUCCESS                                = 15316,  -- That twinkle in your eye... Is that success I sense?
        YOUR_PLEASE                                                             = 15317,  -- Your %, please!
        YES_THE_DATA_FOR_THE_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_HAS                              = 15318,  -- Yes, the data for the geomagnetic fount has been recorded properly.
        FROM_RECORDING_TO_FIXING_IS_THERE_NOTHING_THAT                          = 15319,  -- From recording to fixing...is there nothing that adventurers cannot do? Here, a token of my esteem.
        WELL_WOULD_YOU_LOOK                                                     = 15320,  -- Well, would you look...
        I_AM_QUITE_PLEASED_TO_SEE_THAT_YOU                                      = 15321,  -- I am quite pleased to see that you have returned whole.
        DO_NOT_BE_WORRIED_THOUGH_YOU_MAY_NOT                                    = 15322,  -- Do not be worried. Though you may not have succeeded this time, the important thing is the waypoints did not spell out your demise.
        IT_IS_MY_UNDERSTANDING_THAT_YOU_DEIGN_TO                                = 15323,  -- It is my understanding, %, that you deign to serve as a pioneer in Adoulin.
        OH_YES_NOT_ONLY_DO_I_HAVE_EARS                                          = 15324,  -- Oh yes, not only do I have ears everywhere, but I can see that glowing % you hold in your very hands.
        MY_GRANDDAUGHTER_GUIDES_THOSE_NEW_TO_ADOULIN_INSTRUCTING                = 15325,  -- My granddaughter guides those new to Adoulin, instructing them in the mysteries of waypoints. Please, give her my regards if you meet her by happenstance.
        SHE_IS_A_SWEET_GIRL_VERY_REFINED_THANKS                                 = 15326,  -- She is a sweet girl, very refined, thanks largely to her strict upbringing. I am sure that she will provide you with any assistance you should require.
        WHY_WHAT_A_MOST_PLEASANT_SURPRISE_HOW_CAN                               = 15327,  -- Why, %! What a most pleasant surprise. How can I help you this fine... What's this? A present from my beloved Alienor?
        WHAT_A_THOUGHTFUL_YOUNG_LADY_SHE_HAS_GROWN                              = 15328,  -- What a thoughtful young lady she has grown up to be, making me such a delectable treat.
        YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_MORE_ABOUT_HOW_OUR                                     = 15329,  -- You wish to know more about how our research is going? Well, to be frank...I have not received word from [Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison] of late.
        I_HESITATE_TO_ASK_THIS_OF_YOU_SINCE                                     = 15330,  -- I hesitate to ask this of you, since I am certain you have other pressing matters to attend to, but would you deliver some of this % to [Selbina/Mhaura/Rabao/Norg] for me?
        THE_ENCHANTING_SMELL_OF_BRINE_UPON_THE_WIND                             = 15331,  -- The enchanting smell of brine upon the wind... A tantalizing dish from a devoted granddaughter... What more is there to life?
        THERE_IS_ALWAYS_A_SNAG_SOMEWHERE_WITH_COMPLICATED                       = 15332,  -- There is always a snag somewhere with complicated operations such as the one we are engaged in here. This time, I have not received word from [Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison].
        THANK_YOU_FOR_CHECKING_UP_ON_I_AM                                       = 15333,  -- Thank you for checking up on [Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison]. I am relieved to hear that all is well.
        PLEASE_TELL_ALIENOR_THAT_I_AM_GRATEFUL_FOR                              = 15334,  -- Please tell Alienor that I am grateful for her gift and that the people here in Jeuno are treating me with the utmost kindness.
        A_WAYPOINT_LIES_BEFORE_YOU_IN_ALL_ITS                                   = 15335,  -- A waypoint lies before you in all its mystery.
        YOU_WERE_UNABLE_TO_WARP_TO_YOUR_DESIRED                                 = 15336,  -- You were unable to warp to your desired destination.
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_KINETIC_UNITS_NOTHING_READ                             = 15337,  -- What will you do? (Kinetic Units: #) Nothing. Read an explanation! Go to Western Adoulin. Go to Eastern Adoulin. Go to Ceizak Battlegrounds. Go to Yahse Hunting Grounds. Go to Foret de Hennetiel. Go to Morimar Basalt Fields. Go to Yorcia Weald. Go to Marjami Ravine. Go to Kamihr Drifts. Go to Jeuno. (# unit[/s]) Go to an enigmatic device. Use runes. Decline destination confirmation. Accept destination confirmation.
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_KINETIC_UNITS_NOTHING_READ_2                           = 15338,  -- What will you do? (Kinetic Units: #) Nothing. Read an explanation. Go to Western Adoulin. (# unit[/s]) Decline destination confirmation. Accept destination confirmation.
        CHOOSE_A_DESTINATION_KINETIC_UNITS_BACK_NORTHERN_SAN                    = 15339,  -- Choose a destination. (Kinetic Units: #) Back. Northern San d'Oria. (# unit[/s]) Bastok Markets. (# unit[/s]) Windurst Woods. (# unit[/s]) Selbina. (# unit[/s]) Mhaura. (# unit[/s]) Kazham. (# unit[/s]) Rabao. (# unit[/s]) Norg. (# unit[/s]) Tavnazian Safehold. (# unit[/s]) Aht Urhgan Whitegate. (# unit[/s]) Nashmau. (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s]) (# unit[/s])
