        CHOOSE_A_DESTINATION_KINETIC_UNITS_NOWHERE_THANKS_PLATEA                = 15343,  -- Choose a destination. (Kinetic Units: #) Nowhere, thanks. Platea Triumphus (COU Co.). (# unit[/s]) Pioneers' Coalition. (# unit[/s]) Mummers' Coalition. (# unit[/s]) Inventors' Coalition. (# unit[/s]) Auction house. (# unit[/s]) Your Rent-a-Room. (# unit[/s]) Big Bridge. (# unit[/s]) Airship docks. (# unit[/s]) Adoulin Waterfront. (# unit[/s])
