        YOUR_HAS_BEEN_ATTUNED_TO_A_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_7                          = 15350,  -- Your % has been attuned to a geomagnetic fount[/ at the frontier station/ at Frontier Bivouac #1/ at Frontier Bivouac #2/ at Frontier Bivouac #3/ at Frontier Bivouac #4/ at Frontier Bivouac #5]!
