        WHERE_WILL_YOU_GO_KINETIC_UNITS_NOWHERE_THANKS                          = 15371,  -- Where will you go? (Kinetic Units: #) Nowhere, thanks. I'd rather read an explanation. Ru'Lude Gardens. (# unit[/s]) Selbina. (# unit[/s]) Mhaura. (# unit[/s]) Rabao. (# unit[/s]) Norg. (# unit[/s]) West Ronfaure. (# unit[/s]) North Gustaberg. (# unit[/s]) West Sarutabaruta. (# unit[/s]) La Theine Plateau. (# unit[/s]) Konschtat Highlands. (# unit[/s]) Tahrongi Canyon. (# unit[/s]) Jugner Forest. (# unit[/s]) Pashhow Marshlands. (# unit[/s]) Meriphataud Mountains. (# unit[/s]) Attohwa Chasm. (# unit[/s]) Uleguerand Range. (# unit[/s]) Davoi. (# unit[/s]) Beadeaux. (# unit[/s]) Castle Oztroja. (# unit[/s]) Quicksand Caves. (# unit[/s]) Sea Serpent Grotto. (# unit[/s]) Temple of Uggalepih. (# unit[/s]) The Boyahda Tree. (# unit[/s]) Oldton Movalpolos. (# unit[/s]) Riverne - Site #B01. (# unit[/s]) Castle Zvahl Keep. (# unit[/s]) Decline destination confirmation. Accept destination confirmation.
