        BUT_IT_S_NO_GOOD_WITHOUT_THE_BONDS                                      = 15526,  -- But it's no good. Without the bonds, we just can't do it! The closest we've come is to craft ciphers--magical parchments that concentrate energies from a third party into physical forms. But that's the rub: it still requires those bonds in the first place.
