        STILL_I_PROMISE_THE_JOURNEY_WILL_BE_WORTH                               = 15535,  -- Still, I promise the journey will be worth it...for you, and for us.
        BONDS_CANNOT_BE_SEVERED_LIKE_A_HOT_KNIFE                                = 15536,  -- Bonds cannot be severed like a hot knife cutting through Selbina butter. The key is whether or not the strengths of the bonds' creators are enough to survive transcription.
        IF_THERE_S_SOMEONE_WHO_YOU_FEEL_A                                       = 15537,  -- If there's someone who you feel a strong connection with, what can it hurt to ask them for their cooperation? You'll never know until you try!
        HELLO_CAN_I_HELP_YOU                                                    = 15538,  -- Hello. Can I help you?
        HM_YOU_RE_HERE_ABOUT                                                    = 15539,  -- Hm? You're here about %?
        I_M_SORRY_YOU_CAME_ALL_THIS_WAY                                         = 15540,  -- I'm sorry you came all this way, but I've already been briefed on that particular topic.
        WAIT_JUST_A_MOMENT_AH_NOW_I_REMEMBER                                    = 15541,  -- Wait just a moment. Ah, now I remember you. Yes, I've been looking for you ever since our last encounter. Now, I need you in the field to help with my research...
        AH_FORGIVE_ME_I_WAS_SO_EXCITED_TO                                       = 15542,  -- Ah, forgive me. I was so excited to find the person I was looking for, I forgot to explain what it is I'm doing.
        I_VE_HEARD_FROM_A_COLLEAGUE_THAT_MY                                     = 15543,  -- I've heard from a colleague that my research into Trust magic has earned the recognition of an academic organization.
        THEY_HAVE_EVEN_GIVEN_ME_CLEARANCE_TO_READ                               = 15544,  -- They have even given me clearance to read their most confidential documents in pursuit of my research. Well, a portion of them at least.
        HOWEVER_WHEN_COMPARING_THAT_INFORMATION_AGAINST_WHAT_I                  = 15545,  -- However, when comparing that information against what I had gathered, I came across some interesting discoveries.
        FOR_EXAMPLE_I_LEARNED_THAT_YOU_HAD_DEFEATED                             = 15546,  -- For example, I learned that you had defeated an unusual life-form considered to be the physical embodiment of the darkest parts of a person's soul.
        THEN_IT_STRUCK_ME_A_NEW_LINE_OF                                         = 15547,  -- Then it struck me--a new line of thought in my Trust magic research.
        THAT_S_RIGHT_I_M_RESEARCHING_THE_TOPIC                                  = 15548,  -- That's right. I'm researching the topic of a dark Trust magic!
        HOW_WILL_YOU_RESPOND_DARK_TRUST_MAGIC_I                                 = 15549,  -- How will you respond? Dark Trust magic? I see where this is going.
        HUH_YOU_MEAN_YOU_DON_T_KNOW                                             = 15550,  -- Huh? You mean you don't know?
        OH_YOU_DO_DO_YOU                                                        = 15551,  -- Oh you do, do you?
        WELL_ALLOW_ME_TO_BRIEFLY_EXPLAIN_THINGS_JUST                            = 15552,  -- Well, allow me to briefly explain things just in case.
        CURRENTLY_THE_TRUST_MAGIC_YOU_USE_IS_BASED                              = 15553,  -- Currently, the Trust magic you use is based on light. It draws on positive forces such as trust, friendship, and brotherly/sisterly] love.
        ON_THE_OTHER_HAND_TRUST_MAGIC_BASED_ON                                  = 15554,  -- On the other hand, Trust magic based on darkness draws upon negative forces to generate its magic, much like how that woman was able to accomplish what she did.
        OH_I_SUPPOSE_I_M_LEAVING_OUT_SOME                                       = 15555,  -- Oh, I suppose I'm leaving out some rather important information. That is to say, an explanation of the negative aspects of mankind's darker side.
        I_M_BASICALLY_REFERRING_TO_THINGS_LIKE_APATHY                           = 15556,  -- I'm basically referring to things like apathy, arrogance, cowardice, envy, and rage. You know, the darkest parts of one's soul. I believe that everybody harbors these feelings, at least to a certain extent.
        IN_A_SENSE_ALL_OF_US_ARE_UNITED                                         = 15557,  -- In a sense, all of us are united by the darkness within our souls. Therefore, it only seems logical to infer that we have the necessary conditions to employ Trust magic from it.
        ALL_THAT_REMAINS_IS_TO_TRY_AND_ELEVATE                                  = 15558,  -- All that remains is to try and elevate the darkness within the alter ego's soul and somehow link up with it...a type of bond all its own.
        ALTHOUGH_EVEN_IF_WE_ARE_UNABLE_TO_UTILIZE                               = 15559,  -- Although, even if we are unable to utilize the Trust magic, we have the % at our disposal. Intimate knowledge of your quarry should enable you to form a bond with them.
        WHICH_BRINGS_ME_TO_MY_REQUEST_I_D                                       = 15560,  -- Which brings me to my request. I'd like for you to test your mettle against those unique forces. However, it cannot be any regular fight. You must really get to know your opponent.
        I_REQUESTED_THE_A_M_A_N_TO                                              = 15561,  -- I requested the A.M.A.N. to create a Records of Eminence objective for this purpose, so it should help you remain cognizant of your opponent during battle.
        HM_YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_HOW_TO_FIGHT                                        = 15562,  -- Hm? You want to know how to fight this particular opponent again? I think you probably know more about that sort of thing than I do.
        YOU_LEARN_MORE_ABOUT_TRUST_MAGIC_AND_I                                  = 15563,  -- You learn more about Trust magic, and I get further along in my research. That's what I call a win-win.
        I_HEARD_FROM_MY_COLLEAGUE_THAT_HE_OBTAINED                              = 15564,  -- I heard from my colleague that he obtained a rather unusual cipher. Perhaps you should see this through to its conclusion?
        AH_IT_S_YOU_AGAIN_IT_SEEMS_EVERYTHING                                   = 15565,  -- Ah, it's you again. It seems everything went rather well.
        JUDGING_BY_THE_MAGICAL_AURA_YOU_RE_GIVING                               = 15566,  -- Judging by the magical aura you're giving off, I'd say we got the results I was hoping for.
        KEEP_IN_MIND_THAT_TRUST_MAGIC_RESEARCH_IS                               = 15567,  -- Keep in mind that Trust magic research is an ongoing process. I must continue my efforts to unlock its mysteries.
        I_M_WORKING_ON_PREPARATIONS_FOR_MY_NEXT                                 = 15568,  -- I'm working on preparations for my next study. Please come by again later.
        HELLO_AGAIN_I_VE_FINISHED_MAKING_THE_NECESSARY                          = 15569,  -- Hello again. I've finished making the necessary preparations. This is the data I'm searching for this time.
        THANKS_AGAIN_FOR_YOUR_HELP                                              = 15570,  -- Thanks again for your help.
        IF_THE_TEST_RESULTS_FOR_THIS_DARKNESS_BASED                             = 15571,  -- If the test results for this darkness-based Trust magic follow my hypothesis, then my next step will be to research Trust magic that combines the power of both light and darkness.
        I_BELIEVE_TRUST_MAGIC_THAT_COMBINES_THE_POWER                           = 15572,  -- I believe Trust magic that combines the power of light and darkness no longer just gives rise to alter egos, but a unique form of existence.
        AN_ALTER_EGO_COMBINING_THE_POWER_OF_BOTH                                = 15573,  -- An alter ego combining the power of both light and darkness... Just think of what this could mean!
        ALTHOUGH_I_M_CURRENTLY_SUFFERING_FROM_A_LACK                            = 15574,  -- Although, I'm currently suffering from a lack of research samples.
        IN_ORDER_TO_SUCCESSFULLY_REALIZE_DARK_BASED_TRUST                       = 15575,  -- In order to successfully realize dark-based Trust magic, I tried replicating the connection that my research was based on, but it is not going so well...
        IF_ONLY_I_COULD_GET_TO_THE_TRUTH                                        = 15576,  -- If only I could get to the truth of the matter, it could be like a ticket to eternal paradise without the unfortunate precursor of dying first.
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_SPEAK_WITH                              = 15577,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Rolandienne in Southern San d'Oria (G-10).
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_SPEAK_WITH_2                            = 15578,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Isakoth in Bastok Markets (E-11).
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_SPEAK_WITH_3                            = 15579,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Fhelm Jobeizat in Windurst Woods (J-10).
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_SPEAK_WITH_4                            = 15580,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Eternal Flame in Western Adoulin (H-11).
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_YOU_TO_SPEAK_WITH_5                            = 15581,  -- Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Nantoto in Lower Jeuno (H-8).
        INVISIBLE_EYES_UPON_YOU_CAUSE_THE_HAIRS_ON                              = 15582,  -- Invisible eyes upon you cause the hairs on the back of your neck to rise.
        THE_NODS_IN_AGREEMENT                                                   = 15583,  -- The % nods in agreement.
        A_NEW_RECORDS_OF_EMINENCE_OBJECTIVE_IS_NOW                              = 15584,  -- A new Records of Eminence objective is now available!
        A_NEW_RECORDS_OF_EMINENCE_OBJECTIVE_IS_NOW_2                            = 15585,  -- A new Records of Eminence objective, %, is now available!
        YOU_WISH_TO_EXCHANGE_YOUR_SPARKS                                        = 15586,  -- You wish to exchange your sparks?
        WAIT_BUT_A_MOMENT_HERE_FOLLOW_THIS_COMMAND                              = 15587,  -- Wait but a moment. Here, follow this command--er, compendium to the letter and you should be able to learn a thing or two.
        AH_THIS_ALMOST_SLIPPED_MY_MIND_SHOULD_YOU                               = 15588,  -- Ah, this almost slipped my mind. Should you receive any distinct sorts of artifacts for completing an objective, I will be happy to take them off your hands.
        WORRY_NOT_FOR_I_AM_NOT_OUT_TO                                           = 15589,  -- Worry not, for I am not out to rob you of your glory. Quite the opposite, in fact. I will provide you with a worthwhile reward for collecting them.
        THANKS_TO_YOUR_DONATION_I_NOW_HAVE_IN                                   = 15590,  -- Thanks to your donation, I now have # in safekeeping.
        OHOHOHO_TURNING_IN_SPARKS_I_SEE                                         = 15591,  -- Ohohoho... Turning in sparks, I see.
        HOLD_YOUR_HOARDER_HARES_HERO_HEROINE_I_LOVE                             = 15592,  -- Hold your hoarder hares, hero/heroine]. I love your enthusiasm, but you're not going to learn a thing without a primer. Ahhh, here it is. Have a look-see.
        OH_CRUD_THAT_S_RIGHT_YOU_SHOULD_TRADE                                   = 15593,  -- Oh, crud, that's right. You should trade me any special artifacts you get from completing objectives.
        WHY_WHAT_A_GOOD_QUESTION_BECAUSE_I_LL                                   = 15594,  -- Why? What a good question! Because I'll give you a nifty-difty reward at some point, that's why.
        THANKS_FOR_DOING_WHAT_I_ASKED_NOW_I                                     = 15595,  -- Thanks for doing what I asked. Now I have a total of # from you.
        YOU_WANT_TO_TRRRADE_IN_SPARKS_DO_YOU                                    = 15596,  -- You want to trrrade in sparks, do you?
        LET_ME_WAKE_UP_FROM_MY_CATNAP_FIRST                                     = 15597,  -- Let me wake up from my catnap first... Alright, now rrread this.
        WAIT_WAIT_WAIT_IF_YOU_HAPPEN_TO_GET                                     = 15598,  -- Wait, wait, wait! If you happen to get any purrrticularly interesting items from completing objectives, send them my way.
        DON_T_WORRY_I_M_AS_HONEST_AS                                            = 15599,  -- Don't worry, I'm as honest as a cat when the meat's out of reach. I thought of taking them all for myself...
        BUT_I_DON_T_WANT_TO_MAKE_FUR                                            = 15600,  -- ...but I don't want to make fur fly with the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network, so I'll do my job like a good little kitty.
        GRRREAT_NOW_I_HAVE_FROM_YOU_THANKS                                      = 15601,  -- Grrreat! Now I have # from you. Thanks!
        HM_OH_SPARK_EXCHANGE_OF_COURSE                                          = 15602,  -- Hm? Oh, spark exchange... Of course.
        I_M_NOT_COMPLETELY_SURE_BUT_THIS_MIGHT                                  = 15603,  -- I'm not completely sure, but this might help set some things straight...I guess.
        LET_ME_ADD_ONE_THING_PLEASE_FIND_IT                                     = 15604,  -- Let me add one thing. Please find it within your heart of hearts to give me anything of particular interest you get from completing objectives.
        I_LL_MAKE_IT_WORTH_YOUR_WHILE_I                                         = 15605,  -- I'll make it worth your while...I swear! Just keep at it and I'll be sure to surprise you with a hot, steaming helping of gratitude one day.
        THANKS_FOR_DOING_YOUR_PART_IN_THE_BATTLE                                = 15606,  -- Thanks for doing your part in the battle for love and peace! With this latest addition, I'm now keeping track of # for you.
        RECORDS_OF_EMINENCE_IS_A_SYSTEM_BROUGHT_TO                              = 15607,  -- Records of Eminence is a system brought to you by the caring folks at the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network. Set your own objectives whenever you desire, and fulfill them to receive compensation.
        TO_SET_THESE_TASKS_SELECT_OBJECTIVE_LIST_FROM                           = 15608,  -- To set these tasks, select 'Objective List' from the Quests menu, then choose ones that suit your fancy.
        YOU_WILL_BE_REWARDED_WITH_GIL_AND_SPARKS                                = 15609,  -- You will be rewarded with gil and sparks of eminence, which serve the same function as points, notes, credits, and other such methods of quantifying one's greatness. As an extra incentive, adventurers will earn three times the amount of sparks for completing an objective the first time.
        COMPLETED_OBJECTIVES_WILL_VANISH_FROM_YOUR_QUEST_LIST                   = 15610,  -- Completed objectives will vanish from your quest list unless they are repeatable. In the event that you wish to make room for different objectives, you will need to remove them manually.
        AS_A_COROLLARY_REGARDING_REWARDS_YOU_LL_BE                              = 15611,  -- As a corollary regarding rewards, you'll be blessed with special remuneration once you complete several objectives. Bask in the joy of these pleasant surprises when you can.
        LASTLY_ANY_AND_ALL_ACTS_OF_VANDALISM_DIRECTED                           = 15612,  -- Lastly, any and all acts of vandalism directed against your % are strictly prohibited.
        SHOULD_YOU_BE_FOUND_IN_VIOLATION_OF_THIS                                = 15613,  -- Should you be found in violation of this dictum, the heavens will part and wrath incarnate will descend to mete out justice upon you.
