        UNGH_IT_S_LIKE_EVERY_BONE_IN_THIS                                       = 16128,  -- Ungh... It's like every bone in this tired old body is aching...
        AND_WHERE_DID_ALL_THESE_BRUISES_AND_SCRAPES                             = 16129,  -- And where did all these bruises and scrapes come from anyway?
        AM_I_SICK_OR_MAYBE_IT_S_SOME                                            = 16130,  -- Am I sick? Or maybe it's some kind of ancient curse? Wait, I bet I'm being targeted by an evil assassin!
        I_KNOW_I_SAID_SOMETHING_LIKE_IF_YOU                                     = 16131,  -- I know I said something like If you don't need me, then I'll go help someone else! Is that why that greenhorn adventurer's so mad at me?
        OH_HEY_THERE_YOUNG_UN_IS_THAT_A                                         = 16132,  -- Oh, hey there, young'un. Is that a look of concern on your face I see?
        ARE_YOU_WORRIED_ABOUT_MAAT_YES_ACTUALLY_NO                              = 16133,  -- Are you worried about Maat? Yes, actually. No, not really.
        I_HAD_A_FEELING_YOU_D_UNDERSTAND_MY                                     = 16134,  -- I had a feeling you'd understand my current plight. Yes, you're wise beyond your years.
        IT_S_OKAY_THERE_S_NO_NEED_TO                                            = 16135,  -- It's okay, there's no need to be shy. You can be honest with me.
        AT_ANY_RATE_I_M_GLAD_YOU_RE                                             = 16136,  -- At any rate, I'm glad you're here. I could really use your help with something.
        YOU_SEE_THIS_RATHER_FLASHY_YOUNG_LADY_CAME                              = 16137,  -- You see, this rather flashy young lady came by recently with a Goblin in tow...
        SHE_WAS_TALKING_ABOUT_PUTTING_ON_A_NEW                                  = 16138,  -- She was talking about putting on a new show with some Goblins and that she needed to get stronger.
        THE_PRICE_WAS_MOST_DEFINITELY_RIGHT_AND_SHE                             = 16139,  -- The price was most definitely right, and she was eager enough. Indeed, she would've made a fabulous student, but that outfit of hers...
        ALL_THAT_FABRIC_FLUTTERING_ABOUT_WAS_QUITE_DISTRACTING                  = 16140,  -- All that fabric fluttering about was quite distracting. I simply suggested she go change, but she immediately replied What's wrong with this outfit!? What else should an idol wear!?
        THE_HEART_OF_A_YOUNG_MAIDEN_IS_A                                        = 16141,  -- The heart of a young maiden is a strange thing indeed. Even after all these years, I have yet to understand its many mysteries.
        HM_ACTUALLY_NOW_THAT_I_THINK_ABOUT_IT                                   = 16142,  -- Hm? Actually, now that I think about it... That was when I started feeling under the weather too.
        WELL_I_CAN_T_SAY_FOR_SURE_THAT                                          = 16143,  -- Well, I can't say for sure that there is a connection. Anyway, the favor I want to ask you concerns this young lady, you see.
        I_NEED_YOU_TO_FIND_HER_AND_RETURN                                       = 16144,  -- I need you to find her and return this basket for me. She forgot it in all of the hoopla.
        YOU_SHOULD_FIRST_PAY_A_VISIT_TO_THE                                     = 16145,  -- You should first pay a visit to the junk dealer known as Muckvix in Lower Jeuno. He might know where to find her.
        THE_GOBLIN_THAT_BROUGHT_HER_HERE_WAS_FROM                               = 16146,  -- The Goblin that brought her here was from there, after all. I appreciate your help with this matter.
        PLEASE_FIND_THE_GIRL_THAT_CAME_HERE_TO                                  = 16147,  -- Please find the girl that came here to train and give her back this % for me.
        YOU_SHOULD_SPEAK_WITH_MUCKVIX_THE_JUNK_DEALER                           = 16148,  -- You should speak with Muckvix the junk dealer in Lower Jeuno. He might know something that can help you.
        I_WANT_YOU_TO_FIND_THE_YOUNG_LADY                                       = 16149,  -- I want you to find the young lady that came to train with me and return her %.
        UNGH_IF_THESE_OLD_BONES_WEREN_T_ACHING                                  = 16150,  -- Ungh... If these old bones weren't aching so much, I'd go find her myself...
        SO_YOU_GAVE_THAT_BACK_TO_THE_YOUNG                                      = 16151,  -- So, you gave that % back to the young lady? That's a relief.
        STILL_UNGH_I_M_NOT_FEELING_ANY_BETTER                                   = 16152,  -- Still, ungh... I'm not feeling any better. I tell ya, it's no fun getting old.
        UNGH_IT_S_ALL_RATHER_HAZY_BUT_I                                         = 16153,  -- Ungh... It's all rather hazy, but I guess I caused some sort of trouble?
        I_M_GLAD_YOU_RE_ABLE_TO_REMEMBER                                        = 16154,  -- I'm glad you're able to remember that much, at least.
        WHENEVER_YOU_CLOSE_YOUR_EYES_AND_DRIFT_OFF                              = 16155,  -- Whenever you close your eyes and drift off to sleep, a strange power overtakes you each night. The two of us do what we can to keep it in check...
        WAIT_JUST_A_MOMENT                                                      = 16156,  -- Wait just a moment!
        YOU_CAN_T_JUST_START_SAYING_YOUR_LINES                                  = 16157,  -- You can't just start saying your lines before I even get here!
        OKAY_SHOW_MAAT_THE_PILLOW_IT_S_THE                                      = 16158,  -- Okay, %! Show Maat the pillow! It's the proof we need!
        OKAY_SHADOW_THAT_TERRORIZES_THE_BATALLIA_DOWNS_EACH                     = 16159,  -- Okay, shadow that terrorizes the Batallia Downs each and every night!
        IT_IS_TIME_TO_REVEAL_YOUR_TRUE_IDENTITY                                 = 16160,  -- It is time to reveal your true identity! Ullegore!
        UH_OH_2                                                                 = 16161,  -- Uh-oh!
