        WE_BOTH_KNOW_YOU_QUITE_WELL_YOU_VE                                      = 16184,  -- We both know you quite well. You've made quite the reputation for yourself around here.
        ANYWAY_IN_REGARDS_TO_MAAT_EVERYTHING_WE_TOLD                            = 16185,  -- Anyway, in regards to Maat... Everything we told that girl was made up.
        SHE_D_PROBABLY_FEEL_BAD_IF_SHE_KNEW                                     = 16186,  -- She'd probably feel bad if she knew the truth.
        YOU_SEE_IT_WAS_THE_SHE_MADE_MAAT                                        = 16187,  -- You see, it was the % she made Maat eat that caused that to happen to him.
        MAAT_PROBABLY_MENTIONED_SOMETHING_ABOUT_HER_PAYING_HIM                  = 16188,  -- Maat probably mentioned something about her paying him handsomely to help train her, yes?
        THAT_S_THE_PROBLEM_YOU_SEE_HER_PAYMENT                                  = 16189,  -- That's the problem, you see. Her payment to him was a boiled egg. In fact, I believe it's one you're quite familiar with.
        YOU_MEAN_THE_WORLD_EATER_EGG_THE_AN                                     = 16190,  -- You mean... The World Eater Egg!? The %!? An initial egg!?
        I_M_AFRAID_SO                                                           = 16191,  -- I'm afraid so!
        NOPE_GUESS_AGAIN                                                        = 16192,  -- Nope, guess again!
        WOW_YOU_RE_REALLY_GONNA_MAKE_ME_SPELL                                   = 16193,  -- Wow, you're really gonna make me spell it out for you, aren't ya!?
        ANYWAY                                                                  = 16194,  -- Anyway...
        FORTUNATELY_THE_WORLD_EATER_EGG_HE_ATE_HAD                              = 16195,  -- Fortunately, the World Eater Egg he ate had deteriorated rather significantly. As such, it probably could've been much, much worse for him.
        YOU_SEE_WHILE_HE_WAS_AWAKE_HE_WAS                                       = 16196,  -- You see, while he was awake, he was able to somehow contain the power that radiated from within him.
        BUT_WHENEVER_HE_FELL_ASLEEP_HE_TRANSFORMED_INTO                         = 16197,  -- But whenever he fell asleep, he transformed into that monster, which you saw for yourself.
        HEH_HEH_HEH_ALTHOUGH_THANKS_TO_YOUR_BATTLE                              = 16198,  -- Heh heh heh. Although, thanks to your battle against him, the power of the egg seems to have diminished even further, for now at least.
        YOU_CAN_LEAVE_THE_MATTER_TO_US_WE                                       = 16199,  -- You can leave the matter to us. We'll see that the rest of the egg's power is absorbed and sealed away properly.
        THE_MYSTERIOUS_SHADOW_THAT_S_BEEN_HAUNTING_THIS                         = 16200,  -- The mysterious shadow that's been haunting this place each night shouldn't be a problem any longer.
        HERE_THIS_IS_FOR_YOUR_TROUBLES_I_HAVE                                   = 16201,  -- Here, this is for your troubles. I have a feeling you'll be needing it before this is all over.
        I_VE_GOT_SOMETHING_FROM_SHAMI_AND_SHEMO                                 = 16202,  -- I've got something from Shami and Shemo that they wanted me to give to you. Here you go.
        AFTER_TALKING_TO_SHAMI_AND_SHEMO_I_FEEL                                 = 16203,  -- After talking to Shami and Shemo, I feel like a great weight has been lifted from these tired shoulders.
        I_HEARD_THEY_POSSESS_SOME_RATHER_MYSTERIOUS_ABILITIES                   = 16204,  -- I heard they possess some rather mysterious abilities, but I'm sure glad they were here to help. Heh heh heh.
